apps.title: SHRED: Gym & Home Workouts
apps.description:
SHRED is your personal trainer, reimagined—personalized for you with AI, built by world-class coaches, and trusted by over 2 million people worldwide. Every workout is designed by experts and adapted in real time to your goals, your experience, and your equipment. Perfect for gyms, home gyms, or your living room—wherever you go, SHRED goes with you. Your body. Your plan. Your results.

Featured by Apple, Rolling Stone, Men’s Health, Women’s Health, GQ, PCMag, Business Insider, Goop, Garage Gym Reviews, and others.

PERSONALIZED TRAINING THAT EVOLVES WITH YOU
From day one, SHRED builds your plan around how you move and what you want to achieve. As you train, SHRED’s AI learns your patterns—how hard you push, how you recover, and when to advance or pull back. It automatically adjusts reps, sets, rest, and intensity to match your evolving strength and stamina. Gym or home, beginner or advanced—SHRED scales with you and keeps every workout challenging, efficient, and results-driven.

PROGRAMS ENGINEERED FOR REAL RESULTS
Explore expertly designed training paths in hypertrophy, powerlifting, strength, bodyweight, or sculpting. Every program is crafted by real coaches and refined by data from millions of workouts. Whether you’re chasing size, strength, or definition, SHRED’s system combines proven structure with adaptive progression so you keep improving week after week.

YOUR EQUIPMENT, OPTIMIZED
Have dumbbells, a rack, bands, kettlebells—or nothing at all? SHRED automatically adapts to your setup so you get the perfect workout wherever you train. Update your available gear anytime, and your workouts will instantly reconfigure to match your environment.

TALK TO YOUR COACH
Your coach doesn’t just listen—they lead. Get real-time feedback and guidance as your coach talks you through every workout. Hear precise cues on form, pacing, and intensity. When you’re ready to change things up, talk back to adjust your exercises, switch programs, or get nutrition advice. Whether you want to push harder, recover smarter, or refine your goals, your coach keeps you locked in and accountable—rep by rep.

TRAIN. TRACK. TRANSFORM.
Every workout is part of a bigger plan. Track your volume, consistency, and personal bests across programs with performance insights designed to keep you motivated. SHRED’s visual stats make it easy to see what’s working, where you’re improving, and how your dedication compounds into lasting progress.

COMPETE OR STAY PRIVATE
Join leaderboards, challenge friends, and send cheers—or train quietly on your own. SHRED’s community drives accountability without pressure. Celebrate streaks, share progress, and connect with people chasing their own goals at every level.

APPLE WATCH + HEALTH INTEGRATED
Go hands-free. Log every rep, track heart rate, control music, and sync progress—all from your wrist. SHRED connects seamlessly with Apple Health so your activity, calories, and recovery metrics are always in sync.

MORE YOU’LL LOVE
Studio Classes: HIIT, Yoga, Boxing, and more—led by elite coaches.
Deep Stats: See your progress, milestones, and consistency metrics in real time.
Support That Cares: Real human guidance when you need it.

SHRED PREMIUM
• Tens of thousands of workouts and elite programs
• Expert design and adaptive AI insights
• Talk to your coach for feedback, adjustments, and motivation
• Full Apple Watch experience
• Social competition and community features

Try it free for 7 days, or stay with the free version—no strings attached.

Support: support@shred.app
Privacy: shred.app/privacy
Terms: shred.app/terms

raw_data.releaseNotes:
"Success isn't owned. It's leased. And rent is due every day." — J.J. Watt

— NEW —

Post-Workout Summary: Powered by CoachAI and enhanced with Apple Intelligence, this rich new feature gives you a detailed breakdown of your workout—spotlighting key stats, insights, and personal wins right after you finish. Currently available for users on iOS 26 with an Apple Intelligence-capable device. Rolling out to all premium members in the coming weeks.

— FIXED —

+ Apple Watch Improvements: Squashed several bugs introduced with iOS 26 that affected workout tracking and sync on Apple Watch—everything should now run smoother on your wrist.

Questions or suggestions? Drop us a line at support@shred.app or find us on Instagram or TikTok @shred. That’s all for today—now let’s get after it!

apps.title: Gymshark Training and Fitness
apps.description:
GYMSHARK66 IS BACK: CHANGE YOUR LIFE IN JUST 66 DAYS

Gymshark66 is a 66-day commitment to getting your goals. All you’ve gotta do is choose three daily habits that suit you. Then tick them off, every day, for 66 days.

HOW DO I TRACK MY HABITS?

Download the Gymshark Training App (it’s completely free), sign up to Gymshark66 and choose your three daily habits. Whether it’s 30 mins at the gym or a 30-min walk. 10 mins of mindfulness or 10 pages of a book. And, after 66 days, you’ll have created 3 new habits that are proven to last a lifetime. Not bad, hey?

1000'S OF FREE WORKOUTS

We’ve made our Training App even better to help you along the way. It’s got 1000’s of free workouts, led by your fave Gymshark Athletes, which can be done pretty much anywhere! We’ve even included running plans this year for all your Forrest Gump’ers.

FREE WORKOUTS DESIGNED BY PERSONAL TRAINERS AND ATHLETES

Download the Gymshark Training App for exclusive free workouts led by our team of personal trainers and athletes. There's a better way to train, and it's just an app away.

Your training is unlimited with our entire library of free workouts and plans, so you’ll never feel stuck in a workout rut again. With new workouts added each week, you’ll feel constantly inspired and motivated.

TRAIN YOUR WAY

Customise and personalise your own training plan with moves to suit you and your workout goals. Our free training app has both free gym workouts & home workouts for you to use whenever and wherever you want to workout. Find a fitness coach that works for you or explore the library today.

Searching for the perfect free workout has never been easier. Sort and filter based on the equipment, body part, creator or type of training you feel like. From HIIT to lifting and stretching to functional training, inspiration and motivation comes easy with our training app. Simply search and go.

Create home or gym workout routines that work for you, your goals and your lifestyle. Or check out our top 10 workouts of the day and always know what's trending in the training world. Whatever your goal, at the gym or home, there's a free workout for you.

FOR EVERY LEVEL

Whether you're looking for your 100th workout or just starting out, there's a free workout to suit every level. So, work your way through and see just how much you can achieve. Track every rep, set and workout to monitor your progress and unlock your full potential. After all, your only competition is you.

ONE WORKOUT TODAY, ANOTHER TOMORROW

Spotted the perfect workout for tomorrow with one of our personal trainers? Save your faves and come back to them later. Or if you're halfway through and have something else to do, you can resume a plan at any time. Our training app allows you to make your workout work for you.

WORKOUT AS YOU GO

With free workouts on the go, you can find inspiration using the equipment in the gym, or train from home just using bodyweight exercises. Get inspired by athlete workouts and creator plans or go ahead and customise your own workout by picking your favourite moves from our A-Z library.

FREE WORKOUTS FROM HOME

With a whole host of fitness coach led workouts you can do from anywhere; training is as easy as staying at home. Designed to take up minimal space and with no equipment needed, pick the at-home workout that works for you.

INTEGRATE WITH APPLE HEALTH

Sync your workout data with the Apple Health app to better track your health and wellbeing.

DOWNLOAD THE FREE GYMSHARK TRAINING APP NOW

The Gymshark Training app is a place for the entire conditioning community - all abilities, routines and all training styles. Because even when you train your way, we train together. Download the Gymshark free training app today.

GYMSHARK66 IS BACK: CHANGE YOUR LIFE IN JUST 66 DAYS

Gymshark66 is a 66-day commitment to getting your goals. All you’ve gotta do is choose three daily habits that suit you. Then tick them off, every day, for 66 days.

HOW DO I TRACK MY HABITS?

Download the Gymshark Training App (it’s completely free), sign up to Gymshark66 and choose your three daily habits. Whether it’s 30 mins at the gym or a 30-min walk. 10 mins of mindfulness or 10 pages of a book. And, after 66 days, you’ll have created 3 new habits that are proven to last a lifetime. Not bad, hey?

1000'S OF FREE WORKOUTS

We’ve made our Training App even better to help you along the way. It’s got 1000’s of free workouts, led by your fave Gymshark Athletes, which can be done pretty much anywhere! We’ve even included running plans this year for all your Forrest Gump’ers.

FREE WORKOUTS DESIGNED BY PERSONAL TRAINERS AND ATHLETES

Download the Gymshark Training App for exclusive free workouts led by our team of personal trainers and athletes. There's a better way to train, and it's just an app away.

Your training is unlimited with our entire library of free workouts and plans, so you’ll never feel stuck in a workout rut again. With new workouts added each week, you’ll feel constantly inspired and motivated.

TRAIN YOUR WAY

Customise and personalise your own training plan with moves to suit you and your workout goals. Our free training app has both free gym workouts & home workouts for you to use whenever and wherever you want to workout. Find a fitness coach that works for you or explore the library today.

Searching for the perfect free workout has never been easier. Sort and filter based on the equipment, body part, creator or type of training you feel like. From HIIT to lifting and stretching to functional training, inspiration and motivation comes easy with our training app. Simply search and go.

Create home or gym workout routines that work for you, your goals and your lifestyle. Or check out our top 10 workouts of the day and always know what's trending in the training world. Whatever your goal, at the gym or home, there's a free workout for you.

FOR EVERY LEVEL

Whether you're looking for your 100th workout or just starting out, there's a free workout to suit every level. So, work your way through and see just how much you can achieve. Track every rep, set and workout to monitor your progress and unlock your full potential. After all, your only competition is you.

ONE WORKOUT TODAY, ANOTHER TOMORROW

Spotted the perfect workout for tomorrow with one of our personal trainers? Save your faves and come back to them later. Or if you're halfway through and have something else to do, you can resume a plan at any time. Our training app allows you to make your workout work for you.

WORKOUT AS YOU GO

With free workouts on the go, you can find inspiration using the equipment in the gym, or train from home just using bodyweight exercises. Get inspired by athlete workouts and creator plans or go ahead and customise your own workout by picking your favourite moves from our A-Z library.

FREE WORKOUTS FROM HOME

With a whole host of fitness coach led workouts you can do from anywhere; training is as easy as staying at home. Designed to take up minimal space and with no equipment needed, pick the at-home workout that works for you.

INTEGRATE WITH APPLE HEALTH

Sync your workout data with the Apple Health app to better track your health and wellbeing.

DOWNLOAD THE FREE GYMSHARK TRAINING APP NOW

The Gymshark Training app is a place for the entire conditioning community - all abilities, routines and all training styles. Because even when you train your way, we train together. Download the Gymshark free training app today.

▶ Exclusive 28-day personalized dance challenge tailored to your age, BMI, and goals
▶ A wide variety of dance fitness styles: tabata, aerobics, jazz, Latin, hip-hop, high heels, walking dance, and more to make every workout simple and fun
▶ Weekly updated courses for every fitness level, keeping your dance journey fresh

apps.title: Home Fitness Coach: FitCoach
apps.description:
FitCoach - a fitness app for those who want to start a new active lifestyle, build healthy habits, lose weight, get fit, tone up, and feel amazing.

FEATURES:
► Personal training plans
► Step tracker
► Workout history
► Audio prompts during the workout
► Training reminders

WHO IS THIS APP FOR?
The FitCoach app is developed specifically for people who care about their health and want to slim down and get in shape but don’t have enough time to go to the gym.

HOW TO START WITH FITCOACH?
Set your goals: weight loss, muscle gain, or being more active
Select the zone that you want to work on: belly, buttocks, legs, arms.
Enter your personal data such as age, height, weight, fitness level, etc.

HOW DOES IT WORK:
According to your goals and personal data, our intelligent algorithm will suggest a personalized workout plan – a combination of cardio, strength, recovery, and other exercises that will enable you to maximize your results. 
Each week the workout plan will be updated according to your progress and feedback (were the previous workouts too easy or too difficult for you).


FitCoach integrates with the Health app to import Steps data from HealthKit to FitCoach.
FitCoach also integrates with the Fitbit app to import data from Fitbit to FitCoach. 
____________ 

SUBSCRIPTION INFO:
You can download the app for free. Further use requires a subscription. At our discretion, we may decide to offer you a free trial per the terms displayed in the app. Please note that:
When opting for a subscription, you pay the fixed price for your country, which is displayed in the app.
Payment will be charged to your Apple ID Account upon confirmation of purchase.
Subscription automatically renews and free trial automatically converts into subscription unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
Your Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current subscription period.
You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal by going to your account settings on the App Store after purchase.
When canceling a subscription or a free trial, your subscription/free trial will stay active until the end of the current period. Auto-renewal will be disabled, but the current subscription will not be refunded.
In addition to the purchased subscription, we may offer you add-on items (e.g. fitness guides, VIP customer support service) for an additional fee, either one-off or recurrent. This purchase is optional: your subscription is not conditional on such a purchase. All such offers will be displayed in the app.

For more information, see our:
Frequently Asked Questions: https://fitcoach.fit/faq-ios.html
Privacy Notice: https://legal.fit-coach.io/page/privacy-policy 
Terms of Use: https://legal.fit-coach.io/page/terms-of-use

apps.title: SmartGym: Gym & Home Workouts
apps.description:
Achieve your goals faster than ever.

• Apple's Apple Watch App of the Year (2023)
• Apple Design Awards Finalist (2024)
• #1 Health & Fitness app in over 30 countries

FORBES: "Best Apple Watch Apps for Health and Fitness"

Looking for an app to help you work out? SmartGym offers a beautiful, elegant and easy way. With an amazing and advanced algorithm that creates personalized training plans to help you achieve all your goals faster! It's like having a Personal Trainer and a Motivator in your pocket or wrist.

No matter which equipment you have available, SmartGym will always give you the best workout possible, personalized just for you and what you have. Whether you want to lose weight, build muscle, improve your endurance, or just have fun, SmartGym has you covered.

If you're a beginner, SmartGym will help, guide and give you all the confidence you need to start working out. If you're already experienced, SmartGym will give you all the right tools in order to better manage your workouts and track your progress.

● Smart Trainer: Artificial Intelligence able to create personalized workouts that can be done at home or at the gym, based on the equipment you have, the muscles you want to target, and for how long and how often you want to work out. All tailored to your experience level (beginner, intermediate or advanced).

● SmartGym tracks your progress and gives you feedback and tips along the way, like adjusting the number of sets, reps, weight, replacing exercises or even suggesting an entire new routine.

● Track your muscles fatigue after each workout and throughout your entire fitness journey.

● Don't want to use our Artificial Intelligence to create your workouts? That's fine! You can also access over 130 pre-made workouts, carefully created by professionals and curated for you.

● Every workout always adjusted to the equipment you have available.

● Choose from over 690 pre-installed exercises with images and animations, ranging from bodyweight to dumbbells, kettlebells, resistance bands, and more. And if you don't find the one you're looking for, you can always add your own custom exercises with your own images.


More Features:
• Full HIIT Support with Voice Guidance.
• Full Home Workouts support.
• Add as many exercises to your routines as you want.
• Create custom timer for each specific exercise.
• Share your routines with your friends.
• Integration with Apple's Health and Fitness apps.
• Beautiful charts showing all your progress.
• Powerful iPad app.
• SharePlay. Work out together with your friends and family using FaceTime.


Apple Watch only:
• SmartGym is one of the most advanced Apple Watch app in the world.
• Standalone Watch app. No need to use the iPhone with you.
• Smart Trainer (no iPhone required). With just a few taps, you can get an entire workout created for you, right from your wrist!
• Keep track of your heart rate, distance and calories burned.
• Workouts count towards your activity rings.
• Use Siri to start your workout.
• Modify your exercise right from the Watch.


Personal Trainer Only:
• Use Augmented Reality to analyze your students' posture. (A12 device or later is required for this feature)
• Siri Shortcuts with Parameters. Quickly get your student's routines with just your voice.
• Great way to manage all your students.


Subscriptions Details:
The free version of SmartGym gives access to 2 routines, 3 workouts and 2 measures. Upgrade to our monthly or annually subscriptions to access all our features.

Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hour prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication.

This is one of the biggest updates we've ever done. It's packed with awesome new features.

COMPLETE SUPPORT FOR IOS 26 IPADOS 26 AND WATCHOS26
SmartGym has been updated to support all the new systems.

LIQUID GLASS COMPLETE REDESIGN
SmartGym has been completely reimagined with Apple’s new design language, bringing a stunning look and feel across iOS, iPadOS, and watchOS.

SUPPORT FOR NEW AIRPODS PRO HEART RATE SENSOR
No Apple Watch? No problem. With the latest AirPods Pro or Powerbeats Pro 2, you can now track your heart rate (including heart rate zones) and calorie burn directly from your workouts. It’s the perfect option if you don’t own an Apple Watch or simply prefer training with your iPad.

APPLE INTELLIGENCE
SmartGym now integrates with Apple Intelligence through Foundation Models, Apple’s on-device large language model. This makes your experience smarter, context-aware, and tailored just for you.
All the features below are powered by Apple Intelligence and require devices that support it. To enable them, go to More > Apple Intelligence.

IMPORT FROM TEXT
Copy a workout in plain text from ChatGPT or any other tool, then paste it into SmartGym. Smart Trainer (our Artificial Intelligence) works with Apple Intelligence to instantly transform it into a fully functional workout.

SMART GREETING
On the main screen (Routines tab), you’ll be welcomed with a personalized motivational message at the top, generated from your fitness data and goals.

CUSTOM GOALS INSIGHTS
With a single tap, SmartGym analyzes your progress and turns it into clear, actionable insights. See how close you are to reaching your milestones, where you’re excelling, and what you can focus on next to push even further.

MONTHLY SUMMARY INSIGHTS
Your month at a glance, reimagined. SmartGym now breaks down your training, summarizing all your progress. Easily switch between months to spot long-term progress and celebrate just how far you’ve come. Every summary feels like your own personal fitness report card.

ROUTINE PROGRESS INSIGHTS
Go beyond basic tracking. SmartGym now dives deep into each routine, showing detailed insights into your performance, improvements, and consistency. Instantly see how your effort is paying off.

AI PERSONALITY
Everyone is motivated differently. Some thrive on high-energy encouragement, others prefer a steady, balanced push, while some respond best to tough love. With AI Personalities, you can choose the coaching style that fits you best.

ALARMKIT
On the iOS or iPadOS app, go to More > Alarms and set up alarms scheduled to trigger at specific times, even overriding silent mode or Focus settings if needed. Perfect for setting gym-time reminders.

LIVE ACTIVITY AND DYNAMIC ISLAND
The new Live Activity and Dynamic Island design brings richer visuals, real-time stats, and smarter updates right to your Lock Screen or the top of your iPhone. Whether you’re lifting, running, or resting, you’ll always have the info you need, without ever opening the app.

iPADOS
SmartGym feels more powerful than ever on iPad. With Apple’s new flexible window sizing, you can keep SmartGym open alongside your favorite apps, plan workouts while watching videos, or check your stats while browsing the web.


-----

WATCHOS

LIQUID GLASS
The Apple Watch app has also been redesigned with the new design language, bringing a sleek, modern look to your wrist.

SMART STACKS
SmartGym automatically surfaces in Smart Stacks whenever the system knows it’s most relevant to you.

CONTROL CENTER
Add SmartGym directly to your Apple Watch Control Center. Start a workout instantly—no matter where you are on your watch.



If you enjoy using SmartGym, please consider leaving a review on the App Store. It really helps.

If you experience any issues or have any questions, please get in touch with us at support@smartgymapp.com.

apps.title: Bodybuilding.com - Fitness App
apps.description:
Welcome to the new Bodybuilding.com app.  

Designed with seven different ways to workout, trackable health metrics, a customized social experience and an in-app shopping hub for your supplements needs, the BBCOM app is the key to unlocking your true potential. Though don’t just take our word for it. Dive into why you should download the Bodybuilding.com app now.

1. Choose Your Workout Experience  
Follow along with guided workouts led by our coaches, choose an accessory, dive into a multi-week program, design your own workout/progrram, stack your experiences, or learn new moves with our movement library. There’s a way to work out for everyone. 
 
Our team of Master Coaches consists of accredited professionals with decades of experience. They’ll lead multiple modalities ranging from strength and hypertrophy to body recomp and performance. Need a time out? Pause a workout at any time to watch the movement tutorial without exiting. Time for a rest day? Jump into an accessory to take a breathwork, stretching or mobility sequence.  
 
Take planning into your own hands by constructing a workout or program specific to you. Build out your calendar using the move library or stack pre-existing workouts together. Find your routine with endless possibilities.

2. Connect With Likeminded Users
Chasing goals requires support, and when it comes to finding support, community is king. Build your profile, share content, and scroll the feed to find your favorite lifters, workouts, and accounts. 
 
Don’t want to share with the world? No sweat. Set your profile to private and accept invites when they come. You’ll be able to like, comment, share and save content in your feed. Stay tuned for our “Groups” feature coming in 2025- where locals can plan meetups IRL, because nothing beats training together.

3. Track Metrics and Store Data
Stored in your profile, connect to Health Kit or Google Health Services to stay on top of heart rate, calories, and other key metrics. Trying to break down your splits? “Blue Man” is here to help track which muscle groups you’ve worked this week to help inform your next workout selection. 
 
We’ll be revealing fitness devices eligible for syncing in 2025.

4. Earn Badges and Rewards
It’s true, we’re all still utterly obsessed with collecting badges, and you can collect a set of your very own in the app. From “total weight lifted” milestones, to streak celebrations and limited-edition holiday badges, there’s a new goal to chase every month. Don’t worry, we reward recovery warriors, too.  
 
Be on the lookout for future badge releases. Have a concept? Hit up our team to bring your badge to life.

5. Shop Supplements
Yes, you’ll be able to shop for your favorite supplements directly in the app. Did we mention it’s as easy as one click? Annual members will be eligible to year-round free shipping on orders, 10% off our Signature™ line (+ ALL its new products), and if you join now, you’ll earn a $49.99 product coupon to kickstart your journey.  The ease of merging supps with your workout plan is here.  
 
Later this year we’ll be activating a feature that helps you track when it’s time to restock based on your workout routine.

== Subscriptions and Terms ==
The Bodybuilding.com Fitness app offers two auto-renewing All-Access subscription options: monthly and yearly plans.

Annual: $59.99
Monthly: $9.99

The subscription is auto-renewable. This means that it will automatically renew unless you turn off auto renewal in account settings in the App Store after purchase. We also offer a one month free trial to new subscribers so that they can start making gains right away.

Terms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/

apps.title: Lose It! – Calorie Counter
apps.description:
Lose It! is a calorie counter and weight loss diet progress tracking app that helps you stick to your diet and reach your weight loss goals! Simply set your weight loss goals then track your diet, food and exercise to lose weight. Lose It! is more than just a free calorie tracker. You can track your nutrition, macros, carb and calorie intake, and plan your intermittent fasting schedule. Counting calories, tracking your food and losing weight has never been easier!

SIMPLIFY YOUR WEIGHT LOSS JOURNEY
Lose It! uses the proven principles of calorie counting, food tracking, calorie deficit and diet tracking to help you succeed. To get started on your weight loss journey, input your profile details and we’ll calculate the daily calorie budget and schedule . Then, easily track your food, weight, and activity to celebrate your weight loss victories. Change your calorie intake and dieting habits while learning about your nutrition needs to set achievable goals.

AI VOICE & PHOTO MEAL LOGGING
Quickly and accurately log meals using your voice or a photo. Just speak into your phone or tap the camera icon to track food and count calories in seconds. Snap a photo, log a meal and make your weight loss journey simple!

LOSE IT! BASIC FEATURES
• Calorie Tracking – Utilize the calorie counter to  it easy to track meals and exercise directly from your phone
• Weight Loss Plan – Build a weight loss plan based on your unique body composition, activity level and habits
• Community Support – Add your friends and join support groups to stay motivated

PREMIUM PLAN FEATURES
• Photo Meal Logging – “Snap It” lets you log meals by taking a picture
• AI Voice – Just say “I had 2 eggs, toast with butter and jam.” to log your meal
• Barcode Scanner – Scan food barcodes or search our database of items and recipes
• Advanced Tracking – track more than just calories including macronutrients like protein, carbs, fat, sugar; as well as health goals, including blood pressure, glucose, cholesterol, body measurements, sleep cycles and more
• Intermittent Fasting - set your intermittent fasting plan and track your fasts in the same app where you track your food
• Meal Planning & Targets – meal targets help you calculate suggested nutritional content including macro, carb, protein and overall calorie intake. Customize your diet and eating style for personalized weight loss!
• Weight Loss Diet Plans – access exclusive personal insights to identify what is hindering or helping your weight loss progress
• Fitness App Syncs – connect fitness trackers, workout apps, and devices like Fitbit trackers, Misfit trackers, Garmin trackers, Withings scales, Google Fit, Healthkit, and more to maximize your weight loss, gain or maintenance goals

Since our launch in 2008 we have been featured in The Wall Street Journal, The Today Show, Men’s Health, Women’s Health, CNET, Buzzfeed, CNN, Shape, Good Morning America, and more.

Lose It! has helped over 57 million users lose more than 150 million pounds. With a global food database of 56+ million items and recipes, tracking what you eat is simple and accurate. Choose from over 25 health goals—including macros, carbs, protein and calories—and start seeing results in just three days of consistent tracking.

Download Lose It! and join our weight loss community, full of members helping us reach our mission to mobilize the world to achieve a healthy weight. No matter your diet needs or weight loss goals, Lose It! can help you find weight loss that fits!

Should you choose to purchase a Premium or Boost subscription, subscription purchase will be charged to your iTunes account. The yearly subscription will automatically renew unless the auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the period subscription ends. Your premium subscription auto-renew can be turned off or managed in your iTunes account settings. Any unused portion of the free trial is forfeited after purchase.

Full terms:
http://loseit.com/terms

Lose It! Is the #1 app for improving your health and reaching your goals.


Food Tracking Made Easy
Whether you're looking to lose weight, tone up, or just watch what you eat, food tracking is key. With an intuitive interface, best in class barcode scanner, database of over 50 million foods, and calorie schedule that lets you plan to eat more on the weekends, Lose It! makes tracking easy.


A Completely Personalized Program
Everyone's approach is different which is why Lose It! lets you build the exact program that you want. Interested in intermittent fasting? Eating more protein? Fewer carbs? Less sodium? Calorie cycling? Drinking more water? Integrating with your fitness device? Great -- we'll help you build a program that will let you thrive.


And So Much More
Lose It! is a one-stop shop where you can build a logging streak, reach weight loss milestones, track health metrics, learn from healthy living articles, connect with other Lose It! members, and get insights into your behaviors. We're excited to welcome you aboard!

With over 50 million users worldwide, we're helping people reach a healthy weight every day. 

Just the usual this week: fixing bugs and watching our members be amazing! Snack ya later!
raw_data.description:
Lose It! is a calorie counter and weight loss diet progress tracking app that helps you stick to your diet and reach your weight loss goals! Simply set your weight loss goals then track your diet, food and exercise to lose weight. Lose It! is more than just a free calorie tracker. You can track your nutrition, macros, carb and calorie intake, and plan your intermittent fasting schedule. Counting calories, tracking your food and losing weight has never been easier!

SIMPLIFY YOUR WEIGHT LOSS JOURNEY
Lose It! uses the proven principles of calorie counting, food tracking, calorie deficit and diet tracking to help you succeed. To get started on your weight loss journey, input your profile details and we’ll calculate the daily calorie budget and schedule . Then, easily track your food, weight, and activity to celebrate your weight loss victories. Change your calorie intake and dieting habits while learning about your nutrition needs to set achievable goals.

AI VOICE & PHOTO MEAL LOGGING
Quickly and accurately log meals using your voice or a photo. Just speak into your phone or tap the camera icon to track food and count calories in seconds. Snap a photo, log a meal and make your weight loss journey simple!

LOSE IT! BASIC FEATURES
• Calorie Tracking – Utilize the calorie counter to  it easy to track meals and exercise directly from your phone
• Weight Loss Plan – Build a weight loss plan based on your unique body composition, activity level and habits
• Community Support – Add your friends and join support groups to stay motivated

PREMIUM PLAN FEATURES
• Photo Meal Logging – “Snap It” lets you log meals by taking a picture
• AI Voice – Just say “I had 2 eggs, toast with butter and jam.” to log your meal
• Barcode Scanner – Scan food barcodes or search our database of items and recipes
• Advanced Tracking – track more than just calories including macronutrients like protein, carbs, fat, sugar; as well as health goals, including blood pressure, glucose, cholesterol, body measurements, sleep cycles and more
• Intermittent Fasting - set your intermittent fasting plan and track your fasts in the same app where you track your food
• Meal Planning & Targets – meal targets help you calculate suggested nutritional content including macro, carb, protein and overall calorie intake. Customize your diet and eating style for personalized weight loss!
• Weight Loss Diet Plans – access exclusive personal insights to identify what is hindering or helping your weight loss progress
• Fitness App Syncs – connect fitness trackers, workout apps, and devices like Fitbit trackers, Misfit trackers, Garmin trackers, Withings scales, Google Fit, Healthkit, and more to maximize your weight loss, gain or maintenance goals

Since our launch in 2008 we have been featured in The Wall Street Journal, The Today Show, Men’s Health, Women’s Health, CNET, Buzzfeed, CNN, Shape, Good Morning America, and more.

Lose It! has helped over 57 million users lose more than 150 million pounds. With a global food database of 56+ million items and recipes, tracking what you eat is simple and accurate. Choose from over 25 health goals—including macros, carbs, protein and calories—and start seeing results in just three days of consistent tracking.

Download Lose It! and join our weight loss community, full of members helping us reach our mission to mobilize the world to achieve a healthy weight. No matter your diet needs or weight loss goals, Lose It! can help you find weight loss that fits!

Should you choose to purchase a Premium or Boost subscription, subscription purchase will be charged to your iTunes account. The yearly subscription will automatically renew unless the auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the period subscription ends. Your premium subscription auto-renew can be turned off or managed in your iTunes account settings. Any unused portion of the free trial is forfeited after purchase.

apps.title: Freeletics: Workouts & Fitness
apps.description:
Europe’s #1 fitness app lets you work out anytime, anywhere with the best digital personal trainer - no gym required. Whatever your fitness level, achieve your goals quickly and build healthy habits with personalized HIIT workouts and audio coaching. Losing weight, gaining muscle or improving your fitness has never been so simple. 

WHY FREELETICS? 
• Freeletics means freedom. Work on yourself and your fitness free of excuses like time, equipment, space, money or know-how. Join 42 million others doing their workout whenever and wherever they want. 
• See fast results with the most advanced digital personal trainer and effective HIIT workouts. Your AI personal trainer tailors everything to you, learning from each exercise and piece of feedback to create your perfect workout, every time. No two people get the same workout plan - this is fully personalized fitness.
• We follow a holistic approach to fitness and self-development. We combine HIIT fitness, mindfulness, knowledge and motivation to help you perfect your training and build a strong foundation for life-long positive change.

The free version of the app contains 20 HIIT bodyweight workouts, 25 exercises, 20 audio sessions, workout spots and a community of millions. If you want to set yourself up for long-term success with the guidance of a personal trainer every step of the way, you can use the Freeletics Coach with a 14-day money back guarantee. 

What you get by upgrading to the Freeletics Coach:

TRAINING 
• Enjoy your own AI-powered personal trainer, who puts every HIIT workout together based on your experience, goals, fitness level and preferences.
• Travelling or short on time? Need to be quiet? Stuck without equipment or can’t go for a run? No problem. Tell your personal trainer what’s going on and it will adapt your workout to suit your needs.
• Your workout plan will be compiled in a “Training Journey.” Choose from 20 Training Journeys in the app, each with a different fitness focus. Look out for our limited editions by professional athletes.
• Choose your workout style. Whether it’s running, bodyweight HIIT or weights in the gym - or a combination of these - there’s a Training Journey for you. Fitness will never be boring again.
• Progress in your training with thousands of HIIT workout variations and over 180 exercises.
• Control your workout from your Apple Watch and track your fitness data in the Apple Health app.

The Training Coach is included in the Training, Training & Nutrition and Body & Mind bundles.

MINDSET
• Add audio coaching to your personal trainer, helping you build a strong, balanced mindset and find lasting motivation to improve your health and fitness. The perfect complement to your HIIT workouts.
• In 5 to 20-minute sessions, learn how to build habits, boost weight loss, de-stress and improve your focus, training, recovery and sleep. The perfect foundation for real success.
• Courses include focus, stress, sleep, fitness, nutrition and motivation.

The Mindset Coach is only included in the Body & Mind bundle.

SUBSCRIPTIONS & TERMS
We offer 6 auto-renewing subscription options:
• Training (3 / 6 / 12 months)
• Training & Nutrition (3 / 6 / 12 months)

The Nutrition Coach is part of the Freeletics Nutrition app.

Your subscription automatically renews if not cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period. You will be charged for the next subscription period up to 24 hours before the current subscription expires. Manage your subscription and disable automatic renewal any time in your Apple account settings. You have the right to withdraw from your initial subscription within 14 days. By purchasing, you accept our Terms of Use (https://www.freeletics.com/en/pages/terms) and Privacy Policy (https://www.freeletics.com/en/pages/privacy).
 
Contact us at https://help.freeletics.com/hc/ or follow @Freeletics on social media for daily workout inspiration. Your personal trainer is ready.

apps.title: Keelo - Strength HIIT Workouts
apps.description:
KEELO is the high intensity functional fitness (strength + conditioning) program that delivers real, measurable results.

FEATURED BY
•  Apple - Today: Stronger Abs, Best New Updates
•  Men's Health - Best Personal Training Apps
•  Men's Fitness - Best Health and Fitness Apps
•  SHAPE - Best HIIT Strength Training App
•  SELF - 13 Best New Workout Apps
•  Forbes - Top 12 Health & Fitness Apps
•  Cult of Mac - Best Strength Training Apps
•  Elite Daily - 17 Apps for Resolutions

KEELO IS FOR YOU, IF YOU WANT:
•  Strength to lift & carry heavy objects in real life without strain
•  Stamina to climb flights of stairs without feeling winded
•  Endurance to hike long distances without trouble
•  Physical independence throughout your life

MORE ABOUT KEELO

FULL BODY WORKOUT
We combine strength, cardio, and conditioning into one program. You'll work and develop your body's full musculoskeletal, central nervous, cardiovascular, and metabolic systems.

PERSONALIZED PROGRAM
Keelo's AI-based algorithm examines your entire workout history to ensure you're working all parts of the body and getting the most out of your workouts.  We keep the muscle confusion high.

DON’T THINK, JUST DO
We show you exactly what to do. No more guessing: "what workout should I do today?"  Keelo keeps track of your scores and progress.

DO ANYWHERE
At home or gym.  Bodyweight-only workouts included.  Some gym equipment, e.g. barbell, dumbbells, kettlebells, recommended.  But don’t worry.  If you don’t have equipment, let us know.  We’d be happy to suggest alternatives!

LEADERBOARDS
See how well you've done compared to others in your peer group!

FREE COACHING BY EMAIL
Email your coach at coach@keelo.com at any time to ask questions about workouts, alternative movements, weight selection, and more.  We want you to succeed.

COACHING BY CHAT (PREMIUM)
Chat with your coach to get faster responses to your workout questions.

APPLE HEALTH
With your permission, we sync your calories burned and workout time with Apple Health.  If completed through an Apple Watch, we also record your heart rate during the workout.

More Features:
•  HD instructional videos for all movements.
•  All workouts scalable to beginners and experienced alike.
•  Works with most Bluetooth heart rate monitors.
•  No login required. Just open the app and go.
•  New workouts added regularly.

_____________________

ABOUT KEELO PREMIUM SUBSCRIPTION

Keelo is free to download and use. To further your training plan and variety, Keelo Premium provides coaching, programming, strength, warm ups, cool downs, and unlocks all workouts.

Keelo Premium plans begin with a two-week free trial for new members. If you cancel during this trial period, you will not be charged. If you continue with your plan, payment will be charged to your App Store account at confirmation of purchase. (USD $12.99 for monthly, USD $30.99 for quarterly, USD $93.99 for annually.) Any unused portion of the free trial period will be forfeited upon purchase. Your plan will automatically renew within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, unless canceled beforehand. You may cancel your plan or turn off auto-renew at any time by adjusting your App Store settings.

Terms of service: http://keelo.com/tos
Privacy policy: http://keelo.com/privacy

_____________________

PLEASE SAY HELLO

If you encounter any issues, please email us at feedback@keelo.com.  That way, we'll be able to respond directly.  Your feedback helps us fix and improve our app. Thank you!

apps.title: Zing AI: Home & Gym Workouts
apps.description:
Zing is the ultimate AI Coach, revolutionizing fitness with AI-powered, personalized workouts designed by top health and fitness experts. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced athlete, Zing AI Coach adapts to your needs, offering real-time insights and support for a transformative fitness journey.

Advanced AI Coach

The AI Coach engages proactively, suggesting goals, scheduling workouts, and providing real-time form monitoring and feedback. It checks in daily about your energy levels, mood, and sleep, adjusting your workout plan in real-time to ensure continuous improvement.

Zing Vision

Our advanced Zing Vision technology uses your smartphone's camera to track movements in real-time, providing detailed insights to improve your technique.

AI Body Scan

Zing's AI Body Scan analyzes your body composition using your smartphone's camera. Receive insights into body fat, lean mass, and more, integrated into your fitness plan for a hyper-personalized experience. Photos are promptly deleted for privacy.

Hyper-Personalized Plans

Zing creates customized workout plans based on your unique body data, fitness background, and lifestyle. It dynamically adjusts workout intensity and complexity based on your progress, goals, and activity levels. The Strength Score helps you track and enhance your strength training, setting clear goals through increased workout intensity and repetitions.

Dynamic AI Workout Progression

Zing's AI adjusts your workout intensity and complexity continuously. Centralize all your activity data in Zing for detailed fitness insights. Seamlessly integrate with Apple Watch and Apple Health. Track your daily activity, earn milestones, and share achievements with friends for added encouragement.

World-Class Training

Zing Coach generates intuitive workouts from almost 500 exercises, adapting to your preferences and goals. It tracks muscle fatigue levels, ensuring safe and effective training sessions.

Diverse Workout Types

Zing offers various workout types including strength, HIIT, stretching, and recovery, with Pilates and yoga coming soon. Each type is designed to enhance different aspects of fitness, from muscle development and fat burn to flexibility and mind-body connection.

Fitness and Flexibility Tests

Take the Fitness Test to assess your current fitness level and the Flexibility Test to measure your mobility. Get personalized insights for your plan based on your results, and improve them with targeted exercises.

Community and Support

Join a vibrant community of over a million users. Participate in monthly challenges, invite friends to your Fitness Circle, and connect with others in our Facebook group. Zing Coach fosters a supportive environment that celebrates transformation and progress.

Subscription Plans

We offer a wide range of subscription options so that you can choose the right one for you (3 months access renewal, weekly renewal, etc.). For your convenience, subscriptions are set to Auto-Renew within the 24-hour period prior to the subscription end date. You can cancel your subscription at any moment in your iTunes account settings, but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the terms. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at purchase confirmation. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable.

Privacy Policy: https://www.zing.coach/privacy-policy 
Terms of Use: https://www.zing.coach/terms-of-use 

HealthKit Integration

Zing integrates with HealthKit, allowing you to export exercise data and import fitness data and body measurements seamlessly.

Contact Us

Email: support@zing.coach
Instagram: @zing.coach

Transform your fitness journey with Zing Coach. Download now and start your personalized training experience today!

raw_data.releaseNotes:
In this version of Zing Coach, there are several quality-of-life improvements, design updates and bug fixes that will make your Zing experience even better.
Get the latest version of Zing Coach to take advantage of these updates!
If you have any feedback or questions, let us know at support@zing.coach. Happy training!

apps.description:
ASANA REBEL - YOGA INSPIRED FITNESS®

---

From losing weight to building strength, from high-intensity workouts to moving meditations: each piece of Asana Rebel is meant to fit every goal into your lifestyle.

One app to help you reach all your health and fitness goals
Asana Rebel will empower you to get in shape, feel better, and stay inspired day after day.

Exercise anytime, anywhere
Be your own gym: work out on your lunch breaks, in hotel rooms, late at night. Explore a world of yoga-inspired programs you can squeeze into the busiest schedules.

Fitness in every format
Make every second count with 5-minute workouts, stay up to date by reading articles, track your progress with daily challenges, get up to date with fun quizzes. Everything to keep you showing up.

Keep your body sharp and your mind sharper
Mindfulness is the ultimate skill to level up your training and boost your productivity. Bring clarity into your workouts with guided sessions and get in the zone with Music for Focus. 

Find a routine that works for you and build lifelong habits
Train smarter, eat better, recover faster. Begin your journey with a single challenge and build from there.
Get moving and stay inspired!


Download Asana Rebel now.

Apple Health integration: Report your calories burned, weight, and yoga workouts (optional)


HOW TO USE THE APP & SUBSCRIPTIONS
The download of Asana Rebel is free. Get all available workouts within the app as part of the monthly subscription. apps.title: JEFIT Workout Plan Gym Tracker
apps.description:
Get Fit and Strong with JEFIT: Your Reliable Gym Planner and Workout Organizer

JEFIT is a trusted workout tracker for iPhone, designed to help you achieve your fitness goals with precision and ease. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned athlete, JEFIT is a versatile fitness plan for the gym or home workouts. With detailed workout programs, HD video instructions, and powerful tracking tools, JEFIT empowers you to log, plan, and optimize your fitness journey.  

Why Choose JEFIT
- Gym Planner & Workout Organizer: Create fully personalized daily workout plans tailored to your goals, whether it's cutting, bulking, or maintaining.  
- Workout Tracker for iPhone: Easily log your weight, reps, and sets, and track your progress with a user-friendly interface.  
- Fitness Plan for the Gym: Access 1,400+ exercises, including barbells, dumbbells, kettlebells, and cardio machines, with detailed instructions and animations.  
- Sync with Apple Health: Integrate your workout data with Apple Health to monitor body weight, height, exercise time, and more.  
- In-Time Training Insights: Gain valuable insights into your daily and weekly training effectiveness, helping you optimize your workouts for better results.  
- 1RM & Strength Tracking: Record your lifting progress and automatically calculate your One Rep Max (1RM) for each exercise. JEFIT supports 1 rep max estimation, advanced 1RM analytics, and strength performance tracking, helping you measure your true strength level and follow progressive overload with confidence.
- Progress & Strength Analytics: Beyond logging sets and reps, JEFIT tracks your max lifting records, monitors 1RM performance trends, and provides data-driven insights into your long-term strength progression. Whether you’re testing a new one-rep max on squats or reviewing weekly 1RM metrics, JEFIT gives you clarity on where you stand.

Key Features
- Extensive Exercise Database: Over 1,400 weight training and muscle-building exercises with HD video demonstrations for proper form.  
- Community-Driven Workouts: Download daily routines and fitness plans created by the JEFIT community or design your own.  
- Smartwatch Integration: Sync with your smartwatch for efficient, on-the-go workouts.  
- Progress Tracking: Monitor your fitness progress, save your best lifting records, and stay motivated with visual improvements.  
- Social Engagement: Connect with friends, share logs, and compare progress with the thriving JEFIT community.  

What’s New
- Apple Health Sync: Keep all your fitness data in one place by syncing with Apple Health.  
- In-Time Training Insights: Understand the effectiveness of your workouts with data-driven insights into your daily and weekly performance.  
- Enhanced Workout Experience: Enjoy smoother tracking, improved analytics, and a more intuitive interface.  

Join the JEFIT Community
With over 10 million users worldwide, JEFIT is trusted by fitness enthusiasts and professionals alike. Whether you're looking to build muscle, lose weight, or improve your overall fitness, JEFIT provides the tools and support you need to succeed.  

Upgrade to JEFIT Elite
Unlock advanced features with JEFIT Elite for $69.99/year:  
- Unlimited smartwatch workouts  
- Professional audio cues  
- Advanced fitness analytics  
- Premium training routines crafted by experts  

Subscription Details:  
- Charges are billed to your iTunes Account.  
- Auto-renews unless canceled 24 hours before the renewal date.  
- Manage or cancel subscriptions in your app store settings.  

Terms and Privacy:  
By upgrading to Elite, you agree to our (https://www.jefit.com/terms-of-use/) and (https://www.jefit.com/privacy-policy/).  

Download JEFIT today and take control of your fitness journey with a reliable gym planner, workout organizer, and workout tracker! Transform your body and achieve your goals with JEFIT!

apps.title: MyFitCoach - Workout Planner
apps.description:
Get your personalized workout plan for effective muscle building now with the MyFitCoach app!


◆ Effective muscle building through science-based strength training:

MyFitCoach applies cutting-edge science to your strength training, selecting the optimal exercises, sets, reps, and weights for you, helping you achieve your fitness goals.


◆ Get a personalized workout plan:

MyFitCoach creates your tailored workout plan to fit your schedule, your available equipment (at the gym or at home), and perfectly aligned with your muscular strengths, weaknesses, and priorities.


◆ Get stronger with every workout:

MyFitCoach gets to know you better with each workout to determine the optimal reps and weights for you, so you get stronger every week.


◆ Learn new exercises & perfect your form:

With our database of 500+ exercises, your strength training will never be boring. Using instructional images and detailed descriptions, you'll learn new exercises in no time and perfect your form over time.


◆ See your progress:

After each workout and week, you will receive a detailed progress analysis, showing how long you trained, how much weight you moved in total, and which exercises you have improved or set new personal records on.


◆ Long-term workout programming:

To ensure long-term muscle growth, MyFitCoach optimizes your training volume based on your performance and recovery.


◆ Apple Health:

Integrated with Apple Health for workouts, body weight, macronutrients, and steps to improve your coaching experience.


◆ Testimonials:

"Building muscle has never been so easy." - Patrick Reiser (World Champion in Natural Bodybuilding)

"I never thought that after 14 years of training, I could still benefit so much from MyFitCoach and not have to worry about training and nutrition anymore." - John Laurent (German Champion Men's Physique)

"Thanks to MyFitCoach, I don't have to worry about my muscle building anymore. Just get your personalized workout plan and try the app in your strength training!" - Mischa Janiec (Pro Natural Bodybuilding)


◆ Subscriptions:

MyFitCoach is available for free download. To use the app, an active subscription is required, available monthly, quarterly, or annually. Subscribers will be charged for the selected period after purchase.

The charge will be made after purchase confirmation through your iTunes account. The subscription automatically renews unless it is canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the billing period.

Subscriptions can be managed in iTunes account settings and auto-renewal can be turned off. There will be no refunds for any unused portion of the term. Any unused portion of a free trial period (if offered) will be forfeited when a subscription is purchased.

Privacy Policy: https://www.myfitcoach.app/privacy
Terms of Service: https://myfitcoach.app/terms

In this update, we've made various minor optimizations (iOS 26) and bug fixes. Additionally, we've made preparations for the next major update.

Enjoy the new update, and if you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us via the support chat in the app.

We're looking forward to your feedback!

apps.title: Mi Fitness (Xiaomi Wear Lite)
apps.description:
Combining Mi Fitness with smartwatch or smartband devices, users can track their health and fitness data. 

Mi Fitness supported：Xiaomi Watch Series, Redmi Watch Series, Xiaomi Smart Band Series, Redmi Smart Band Series.

Keep track of your workouts 
Map your route, monitor your progress, and achieve your goals. Whether it's walking, running, or biking, you can easily track it right from your phone.
Monitor your health information*
Mi Fitness APP assists you in managing your personal health, helping you to always maintain your optimal state. By connecting Xiaomi or Redmi smartwatch/band devices, important health indicators such as heart rate, sleep, stress, and energy can be monitored and risk warnings generated throughout the day. Health data such as weight and women's health can also be manually recorded and managed.
Sleep better*
In conjunction with Xiaomi or Redmi smartwatch/band devices that has sleep monitoring functionality, you can record your sleep information every night. By conducting in-depth analysis of the different stages of sleep, including deep sleep, light sleep, and rapid eye movement, as well as monitoring your sleep heart rate, breathing quality, body movements, and other sleep-related data, the device generates a personalized sleep report. This report can help remind you to adjust your sleep habits in a timely manner.
Easy payments with wearable device
Link your Mastercard cards to Mi Fitness and enjoy the convenience of making payments on the go with your wearable device.
Ask Alexa for convenient access
With Alexa, you can easily access important features like checking the weather, playing music, and starting a workout. Just ask and you're good to go.
Stay informed with notifications
Receive notifications, messages, and emails directly on your wearable device, so you can stay informed without having to constantly check your phone.

*Disclaimer
Except for the manual health information recording service provided to users, all other health services within the application only synchronize and record the relevant information of the wristband or watch. All health-related data, results, suggestions, etc. are for reference only and are not intended for medical purposes, including self-diagnosis or consultation with a doctor, and are only used for general fitness and health purposes.
Please note that all smartwatches/fitness trackers currently integrated into the application are not medical devices and cannot provide any form of medical services. In case of any physical discomfort, please seek timely advice from medical institutions.

All health-related data, results, suggestions, etc. are for reference only and are not intended for medical purposes, including self-diagnosis or consultation with a doctor, and are only used for general fitness and health purposes.
Please note that all smartwatches/fitness trackers currently integrated into the application are not medical devices and cannot provide any form of medical services. In case of any physical discomfort, please seek timely advice from medical institutions.

apps.description:
Playbook is one of the top fitness apps on the market where you can support your favorite creators directly. THE MAJORITY OF YOUR SUBSCRIPTION GOES DIRECTLY TO THE PEOPLE CREATING THE WORKOUTS AND CLASSES YOU LOVE. Get access to the world’s leading fitness influencers, trainers, wellness gurus, athletes, and more all on your phone. With over 56,000 workouts and more than 500 instructors, there is something for everyone to achieve health and wellness goals. Take Playbook with you to the gym; workout at home and even while traveling — with the ability to download workouts you can sweat any time, anywhere.

Premium features:
• Join a community of motivated individuals to help reach your goals 
• Communicate directly with your favorite creators
• Get daily workouts and access to programs and challenges (with prizes)
• Wellness guides for the full experience: Nutrition, supplements, recipes, mindset, productivity, and more 
• Unlimited offline downloads, plus stream to other devices
• Favorite workouts, schedule classes, and track your progress
• Live streaming classes to workout with instructors in real time
• Your subscription money supports your favorite creators directly

Elevate your fitness journey with STNDRD, the premier app designed to help you unlock your full potential. Whether you're aiming to build muscle, tone your body, or enhance overall fitness, STNDRD provides the tools, guidance, and motivation you need to achieve greatness.

Led by the Best in the Industry
Train under the expert guidance of 6x Mr. Olympia Champion, Chris Bumstead (CBUM). His exclusive bodybuilding-focused workout program offers a comprehensive approach to fitness, with detailed exercise information, weight tracking, and nutrition features to ensure you stay on track.

Tailored Programs for Every Level

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Experience a significant upgrade in your fitness journey with The STNDRD App. 

New Features and Enhancements

1. Introducing a brand new Jacklete Program inside the app to elevate your fitness journey with structured workouts designed for optimal results. 
2. Upgraded habit tracking experience to help users stay accountable and measure progress more effectively throughout their Jacklete challenge. 

General Fixes and Improvements

3. Flashlight icon state now correctly updates when switching between rear and front cameras. 
4. Resolved issue where a loader appeared even when the user had no followings in the Following Posts section. 
5. Addressed specific behavior causing UI flickering and unresponsive buttons after permission denial. 
6. Fixed a bug where the app turned into a black screen and became unresponsive after saving notes in the Nutrition module. 
7. Logged food entries now persist correctly when navigating between dates on the Nutrition page. 
8. Serving digits no longer overlap with the serving size text. 
9. Users without access to the Recipe feature no longer see the “Items Added” tile. 
10. Nutrition percentage values on the full nutrition info page now reflect the correct data without resetting to zero. 
11. “Add Food” popup now correctly appears after updating values from a barcode scan. 
12. Fixed an issue where only audio played while the video remained invisible, showing only an image placeholder. 
13. Resolved overlapping sound effects when tapping the “Join Program” button. 
14. New Set Intensifier name now displays correctly during workout execution. 
15. All new intensifiers have been added to the Custom Workout feature. 
16. Fixed an issue where completed programs were incorrectly labeled as “Rest Day” in the Dashboard. 
17. Habit Tracker count is now capped correctly, preventing old badges from reappearing after exceeding limits. 

For any issues or feedback, please contact us at support@stndrd.app

apps.title: Aaptiv: #1 Audio Fitness App
apps.description:
Everyone deserves the benefits of moving smarter. That’s why we created Aaptiv, an AI-powered audio and video fitness app that creates hyper-personalized workout plans and on-demand classes led by expert trainers to help you crush your fitness goals. Whether you’re a fitness guru or just getting started, Aaptiv can create the perfect workout tailored just to you.

FEATURES:
SmartCoach: With Aaptiv, you become the star of your own fitness journey. Our SmartCoach feature, powered by AI, acts as your trusty pocket personal trainer. It starts by asking you a series of questions to understand your age, physical ability, and goals. Armed with this information, SmartCoach creates a tailor-made workout plan that's just right for you. It's like having a dedicated personal trainer that's always by your side, pushing you to greatness!
Audio & Video Workouts: With over 10,000 on-demand audio and video workouts at your fingertips, boredom is simply not an option. Aaptiv covers it all, from running and walking to elliptical sessions, strength training, stretching, yoga, and even rowing. We're constantly adding new classes to keep things fresh and exciting because we believe that variety is the spice of fitness!
Stats: We know that progress is key to staying motivated, so we've included the awesome Stats feature in the app. Keep track of your accomplishments, monitor your improvements, and celebrate your victories over time. It's your personal dashboard of success!
Heart Rate Zone Training: Take your workouts to the next level by pairing Aaptiv with a smart device to measure your heart rate. Our heart rate-based workouts provide on screen feedback, helping you stay in the optimal heart rate zone for maximum effectiveness. 
Programs & Challenges: These multi-week programs are tailored to specific fitness goals, whether you're aiming to conquer a 5K, build some serious muscle, or shed those extra pounds. Stay committed by completing the workouts in the program and watch your transformation unfold!
Music: Need some epic tunes to keep you motivated? Aaptiv has you covered! Choose to listen to your own music while our trainers' voices guide you through the workout, or tap into our specially curated playlists that are guaranteed to get your blood pumping and energy soaring.
Community Feed: Fitness isn't just a solo journey—it's a community-driven adventure! Capture your sweaty selfies and share your progress with other like-minded individuals in our vibrant Community Feed. Get inspired, motivate others, and revel in the support of your fellow fitness enthusiasts.

Get unlimited access to all classes for USD$14.99/month or USD$99.99/year. We also offer a 100% money back guarantee for the annual plan within 30 days, no questions asked.

apps.title: Yuka - Food & Cosmetic Scanner
apps.description:
◆ 70 MILLION USERS ◆

Yuka is a free mobile app that allows you to scan the barcodes of food and personal care products and instantly see their impact on your health. A rating and detailed information help you understand the analysis of each product.

When a product has a negative impact on your health, Yuka also recommends similar but healthier alternative products.

◆ A 100% INDEPENDENT PROJECT ◆

Yuka is a 100% independent project : product reviews and recommendations of healthier alternatives are done in an objective way. No brand or manufacturer can influence them in one way or another. Furthermore, there is no in-app advertising. You can access detailed information on our business model on our website (www.yuka.io).

◆ 5 MILLION REFERENCED PRODUCTS ◆

Yuka established a database that contains 3 million food products and 2 million cosmetic products.

Each food product is evaluated according to 3 objective criteria: nutritional quality, presence of additives and organic aspect of the product.

The method to analyse cosmetic products is based on the analysis of all the ingredients of the product. Each ingredient is assigned a risk level according to the latest scientific data.

---
Terms of use: https://yuka-app.helpdocs.io/l/en/article/2a12869y56

apps.title: Mindbody: Fitness & Wellness
apps.description:
Mindbody is the world’s #1 booking platform for fitness, beauty, and wellness experiences. We encourage people to try new things and find what makes them feel physically, mentally, and spiritually their best.  
Whether it’s a class, salon service, or meditation session, we’ve got options.  
 
With over 40k+ studios around the world, we offer top fitness classes like yoga, Pilates, barre, dance, HIIT, bootcamp, and more. Looking for something along the lines of a massage, hair treatment, or cryotherapy? We’ve got that too. Plus, you’ll find promoted intro offers and last-minute deals—it’s all on the app. 
 
How it works: 
* Download the free app, then create a Mindbody account (or log in to your existing account) to get started. 
* Enter your location at the top of the screen to see local intro offers, price drops, and deals near you.  
* Looking for something in particular? Jump to the “SEARCH” icon at the bottom of the window to find businesses near you. From there, you can type in the desired service or browse popular categories. 
* Need to refine your results? Filter your search by business, class, date, time, distance, or category. You can also sort based on what’s recommended, top-rated or closest to you. 
* Once you select a class or appointment, you can read up on reviews, instructor & service provider bios, and how to get there. You can also choose a business first to learn more about their amenities, schedule, services, location, and pricing. 
* When you’re ready to secure your service, select the “Book” button in the right-hand corner. From there, you will be asked to confirm your payment information. Plug in your info, then hit “BOOK AND BUY” to make it official.  
 
Why you’ll love it: 
* Variety: You’ve got local fitness, beauty, salon, spa, and wellness options in the palm of your hand—you decide what works for you. 
* Value: You'll get the best deals to try a new studio or drop-in on a fitness class without committing to a membership. 
* Verified reviews: Know what people are saying about services before you book, with reviews from verified users.  
  
*Flexible Pricing available in the US only 
  
*Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life

Transform Your Fitness Journey with Fitness Buddy – The Ultimate Workout Companion!

Featured In:
• Chicago Tribune: "It’s like having a personal trainer at home without the cost!"
• ESPN Magazine
• Gizmodo: "One of the best iPhone apps ever."

Achieve Your Health & Fitness Goals with Personalized Workouts, Meal Plans, and Progress Tracking! Fitness Buddy is your all-in-one fitness app for home and gym workouts, weight loss, and nutrition. Access customizable workout plans, hundreds of exercises, and meal plans that fit your goals, whether you're building muscle, losing weight, or staying active.

Tailored Workout Plans Just for You
Choose from over 20+ workout programs, including strength training, cardio, HIIT, and flexibility routines. With 2400+ workouts covering full-body, core, arms, legs, and more, you’ll find a plan for every fitness level. Perfect for gym enthusiasts and at-home workouts!

Easy-to-Follow Workout Guides
Get step-by-step workout instructions, HD videos, and helpful tips to improve your exercise form and stay motivated. Whether you’re new to fitness or a seasoned gym-goer, our guides make it easy to start and progress.

Unlimited Exercise Options
Explore over 2400+ exercises with variations in strength, cardio, HIIT, and flexibility training. Easily filter by equipment, body part, or difficulty to build your custom workout routine. From bodyweight exercises to dumbbells and machines, Fitness Buddy covers it all!

Stay on Track with Health & Weight Loss Goals
Track your progress, calories burned, and weight changes with our easy-to-use fitness tracker. Set goals, monitor your health, and stay motivated. Whether you're aiming for weight loss, muscle gain, or general fitness, Fitness Buddy keeps you on track every step of the way.

Customized Nutrition & Meal Plans for Healthy Eating
Access personalized meal plans to support your fitness journey! Choose from keto, paleo, fasting, and vegetarian diets with calorie and nutrient tracking for each recipe. Easily log and monitor your meals for a balanced, healthy diet that fuels your workouts.

Stay Motivated & Accountable
Connect Fitness Buddy with Apple Health to sync your progress, schedule reminders, and monitor your health metrics. Build lasting fitness habits and stay motivated with personalized insights and fitness calendars to track every workout.

Why Choose Fitness Buddy?
Comprehensive Workout Library – 2400+ exercises for home and gym workouts.
Goal-Focused Plans – Tailored workouts for weight loss, strength, and more.
Easy Nutrition Tracking – Personalized meal plans for every health goal.
Progress Tracking & Motivation – Visual insights to track your health improvements.
Transform your health and fitness journey with Fitness Buddy – the only app you need to achieve your weight loss, muscle gain, or fitness goals.

• Connect with Anytime Fitness Coaches virtually and get the support you need when you need it 
• Connect with the Anytime Fitness community and get the answers to your questions from expert coaches and members 
• Find practical advice and tips on everything from fitness, recovery and nutrition—and everything in between. 

It all starts with a plan. Answer a few questions about your goals and what’s important to you and we’ll take it from there. You’ll receive a plan including workouts, tips for making progress in your journey and weekly challenges that will move you towards your goal. 

Access workouts around the clock—anytime, anywhere. Our digital workouts can be done anywhere you are, helping your goals stay within reach and keep you on track wherever life takes you. You can modify your workouts by duration, location, and intensity plus you’re able to connect with a coach via video chat or messaging making your fitness journey a group effort between you and our team. 

Stay connected on your health journey. With the AF App you can also connect with other Anytime Fitness members and join in on the conversations that matter most to you! Interested in learning about sleep health? Want more info on active recovery? Or maybe you are looking for advice on how to get over a performance plateau—it’s all happening on the AF App. Get answers from expert coaches and members alike and prepare to be inspired by the magic that our community brings. 

Share your fitness stats your coaches. Connect the AF App with the Apple Health App to share your fitness stats with your coach.  Now you can automatically keep your coach up-to-date on your daily activity levels, sleep, resting heart rate and more.

apps.title: Fitplan®: Gym & Home Workouts
apps.description:
Work out at home or in the gym with the largest roster of elite trainers ever assembled. Choose from Olympic athletes, bodybuilding pros, or dozens of the leading names in fitness who are here to motivate you, make you sweat, and help you achieve the body of your dreams. 

Whether you are a beginner or a pro, starting a Fitplan® program is the first step toward being stronger, healthier, and happier than ever before! Working out has never been easier.

“I’ve been a Fitplan® subscriber for over a year. I’ve tried many different plans and trainers. This app is amazing. From the technology down to its friendly design, the app can take your gym game further than you ever imagined. Never has it been easier to be trained by elite fitness instructors at a low price.”

“I am 42, have had a gym membership since my 20’s, and Fitplan® programs has finally inspired me to work out consistently. I imagine it’s mostly due to having a routine and knowing that the correct exercises are being utilized. Wish I had this app 10 years ago!”
 
Get instant step-by-step personal training and bodyweight workouts from the world’s top fitness experts. Lose weight, build muscle and sculpt your physique with Michelle Lewin, Jen Selter, Jeff Seid, Rob Gronkowski, and many more, with new trainers and plans frequently added.

Types of plans that you will find on Fitplan® programs include:

Home workouts
Bodybuilding
Bodyweight
HIIT Training
Booty Training
Weightlifting
Athletic Training
Hypertrophy
Functional Training
Bulking
Shredding and Weight Loss

Choose from dozens of personal training programs, designed by your favorite fitness experts. Work out at the gym, at home, or anywhere life takes you.


Don’t know where to begin or which Fitplan® program to choose? Answer a few questions and we’ll recommend the best plans for you.

Follow our daily workouts with step-by-step HD video instruction.

See how your entire body transforms with your hard work and sweat!

Keep tabs on your weights, reps and time, and watch your results take shape.

Get involved with our community, make friends, and get motivated!

Try Fitplan® app free for 7 days.

Every subscription includes full access to our growing library of 100+ Fitplan® programs.

Access all Fitplan® programs with a subscription membership. Try our collection of single-day workouts for free.

Fitplan® app Links:
Instagram: @fitplan_app
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/groups/fitplancommunity/
Support: support@fitplanapp.com

Note: Cancel any time by visiting settings in the app. If you cancel 24 hours before the 7-day trial is over then you will not be charged. If you cancel during the month period for which you've already paid (up to 24 hours before the next period starts), your subscription will continue until the end of that period.

Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable

View Fitplan's privacy policy at https://www.fitplanapp.com/privacy-policy and terms of use at https://www.fitplanapp.com/terms-of-service

INTEGRATION WITH HEALTH APP

The app integrates with Apple’s Health app to track the following PHR (Personal Health Record) Data; duration, steps taken, calories and distance, and exercise type. Fitplan® and Health app connection can be turned on and off in “Sources” section of Health app and by default is off.
