apps.title: Gym Workout Alpha Progression
apps.description:
Maximize your gains and track your progress with Alpha Progression - the ultimate fitness app.

Our app goes beyond creating a personalized workout plan; it empowers you to track your progress and achieve your fitness goals. With an extensive exercises database and expert recommendations, we provide the guidance you need to embark on an effective muscle-building journey. 

CUSTOMIZED MUSCLE BUILDING WORKOUT PLANS
Experience workout plans backed by science, tailored to your objectives and needs. With Alpha Progression, you can choose your training frequency and target specific muscle groups during your gym workouts. For both men or women, our app generates customized strength training plans to elevate your gym workouts. You can create your own plans for added customization.

PROGRESSION RECOMMENDATIONS
Unlock the full potential of your muscle gains with our advanced algorithm. By analyzing your past workout performances, we provide you with recommendations on weight and reps, ensuring you achieve maximum muscle growth through progressive overload. 

TRACK YOUR WORKOUTS
Make use of our workout tracker with an integrated rep counter, weight lifting and RIR tracker, allowing you to monitor your progress. Our note-taking and log features helps you enhance your strength training. Plus, our convenient rest timer keeps you in sync with your next set.

REACH YOUR WEIGHT TRAINING GOALS AND STAY MOTIVATED
We celebrate your achievements by providing a list of personal records and milestones. That way, we ensure you're constantly inspired and rewarded for your hard work.

VAST EXERCISE DATABASE
With our extensive library of 690 exercise videos, you'll learn and perform each exercise with precision and safety. With our exercise evaluations you'll gain insights into the muscle-building potential of each exercise. Categorized by targeted muscles and equipment, you’ll always find ideal workout plans. 

GET INSIGHTS
Optimize your strength training with our graphs and insights. Visualize your workout history and analyze how your muscle-building and strength training have evolved over time.

COMPREHENSIVE PERIODIZATION
You can structure your weight training workouts in cycles and deloads. Also create a progressive plan where the number of sets and the level of effort (RIR) increase gradually week by week. This approach ensures progressive overload and promotes continuous gains, helping you maximize your results and achieve your fitness objectives.

SHARE YOUR PLANS
Share your workout plans with friends or coaching clients. With us you can easily distribute your plans, allowing recipients to customize them according to their needs.

DATA EXPORT
Export your training data as a .csv file, compatible with apps like Excel. This feature enables you to analyze your workout statistics, easily tracking your progress.

Do you have questions about the app? Please send us an email at info@alphaprogression.com

Terms of service: https://alphaprogression.com/terms
Privacy policy: https://alphaprogression.com/privacy

apps.title: Six Pack in 30 Days - 6 Pack
apps.description:
Want to lose belly fat and get six pack abs for the summer? Start sculpting your abs with this super effective abs workout app. Workouts are suitable for all levels, and you can easily do them at home or anywhere, anytime. Just a few minutes a day to get the sexy abs you have been dreaming of!

Workout Plan with Different Levels
Lose Belly Fat, Rock Hard Abs and Six Pack Abs - these 3 levels of workout plans help you lose belly fat and build abdominal muscles step by step. Whether you are a beginner or a pro, you can find workouts that are suitable for you. Different exercises are prepared every day to keep it fresh and exciting.

30 Days of Workout Routines
Amazing results will be achieved earlier once you set a clear goal. 6 Pack Abs - Abs Workout helps you set exercise goals by providing systematic and scientific 30-day workout routines. Exercise intensity increases gradually, so you can easily make exercising a daily habit.

Your Personal Trainer at Home
Is hiring a personal trainer too expensive? Have no time to go to the gym? 6 Pack Abs - Abs Workout is your personal trainer at home. Based on the high-intensity circuit training principle, these workouts are as effective as gym workouts.

Animations and Video Guides
6 Pack Abs - Abs Workout has been scientifically proven to help strengthen all your abdominal muscles. With animations and video guides, you can make sure you perform each exercise safely and effectively.

Features
*Sync data to Apple Health
*No surprise and hidden charges
*30-day workout routines for six pack abs and a stronger body
*Amazing training for weight management and muscle building
*Exercise intensity increases step by step
*Customize your workout reminders
*Records training progress automatically
*Suitable for everyone, beginners, pro, men, women, teens and seniors

Subscription Terms and Details
- Get unlimited access to all features for USD $9.99/month, USD $39.99/year.
- The payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.
- The subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
- Subscription may be managed and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to Account Settings after purchase.
- The account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.

apps.title: MAC+: Gym & Home Workouts
apps.developer: Mars Spor Kulubu ve Tesisleri Isletmeciligi Anonim Sirketi
apps.description:
Welcome to the MAC+ World! If you believe in sports, fitness and good living in every moment of your life, you are in the right place.

With MAC+, which is open to the use of everyone aiming for a better life with daily sports exercises, whether in the gym, at home or outside, sports are with you whenever you want, wherever you want! Plus it's completely free!

You are closer to your goals with targeted, ever-growing training programs and a large exercise library prepared by MAC trainers who are experts in their fields. Moreover, the outdoor sports experience with MAC communities is waiting for you with MAC+!

Fitness:
•	Whether you are a newbie or experienced, MAC+ has training programs for all levels.
•	Sport is always with you with its ever-growing training library! You can easily reach your goals with dozens of dynamic workouts suitable for all levels in 9 different categories. Moreover, you can open the doors of a better life with the target-specific fitness programs you wish in 4 different categories, from muscle gain to weight loss.
•	With MAC+, you can do home exercises or train in the gym.
•	If you are experienced in sports, you can design your own training series. You can create a weight loss program according to your goal, and you can include exercises that include many weight loss movements in your program.

Workout Categories:
•	Cardio: Cardio workouts that are essential for bodybuilding and fitness
•	Pilates: Instrument and reformer pilates workouts
•	Core: All core specific workouts
•	HIIT: High-intensity interval workouts when you want to increase the tempo
•	Stretching: Stretching workouts that will increase your sports capacity
•	Yoga: Yoga methods to help you relieve stress and relax
•	Dance: Dance workouts to make you feel better
•	Cycle: Cycle workouts, the most popular workout type of cardio

Extensive Exercise Library:
•	Over 500 exercise videos are waiting for you in MAC+!
•	You can search for exercise you want in the library, and you can create your own workout program by accessing how exercise should be done.

Outdoor Sports Experience with MAC Communities
If do sports is essential for your life, but not within four walls, then MAC communities are just for you! You can come together with MAC communities in different parts of the city and run, cycle together if you wish, or experience different and dynamic trainings outdoors with MAC trainers. Plus it's completely free!

Download MAC+ now, step into a better life!

MAC+ IG: https://www.instagram.com/macfitofficial
MAC+ YT: https://www.youtube.com/MACFitTurkiye

apps.description:
FINALLY! A 100% FREE WEIGHTLIFTING APP ACTUALLY WORTH USING!

Whether you’re a beginner or an experienced weightlifter, Stacked will help you gain muscle and strength faster.

With it, you can easily and effectively plan and track your weightlifting workouts and fitness goals.

And unlike most other weightlifting apps, Stacked isn’t ugly, unwieldy, unintuitive, and cluttered with unimportant features that you’ll never use.

Instead, it’s clean, elegant, and streamlined because it was built by weightlifters for weightlifters.

And better still—Stacked is 100% free with no restrictions or hidden upgrade fees. 

Here are just a few examples of why Stacked is special . . .

Create simple or complex workout routines

Choose Imperial or metric measurements

Set weight and rep goals for exercises

Track personal records for all exercises

Change workouts on the fly by adding or removing exercises and sets

Automatically do plate math (always know how to load the bar correctly!)

Automatically back up your data in the cloud

And more!

So, if you’re ready to get more out of your training by successfully planning, tracking, and analyzing your workouts, download Stacked now and start your journey today!

apps.title: ALO Wellness Club
apps.description:
Welcome to ALO Wellness Club. Get the VIP treatment with unlimited fitness, mindfulness, and wellness classes from our lineup of A-list instructors. Achieve your wellness goals with on-demand workouts, expert instructors, and personalized class recommendations that fit seamlessly into your schedule. Once you’re a member of ALO Wellness Club, you’ll have all the tools you need for lifelong wellness. Now let's get to work—see you on your mat. 

WHAT’S INCLUDED
3,000+ on-demand fitness and mindfulness classes 
Access to top-tier instructors, wellness professionals, and celebrity trainers 
New classes added weekly from beginner to advanced skill levels 
Programmed series to meet your fitness and mindfulness goals 
Personalized recommendations based on your interests
Stream anytime, anywhere on desktop, tablet, and mobile 

TRAIN LIKE A VIP 

All you need to do is press play. Here to help set the pace, motivate, and push you beyond your limits, our roster of trainers is one you can rely on to meet any goal—big or small.  

HIT YOUR GOALS 

Whether you’re looking to build strength, increase flexibility, relieve stress, or learn a new skill, there’s a class or series for you. Using our Class Finder, you can sort by style, difficulty, time, and instructor to suit your mood and schedule. 

Choose from thousands of studio-style yoga, fitness, and mindfulness classes, including:

Yoga: Vinyasa, Ashtanga, Hatha, Restorative, Yin, Yoga for Beginners, Kundalini, Prenatal Yoga
Fitness: Pilates, Strength, Sculpt, Cardio, HIIT, Barre, Dance, Core Workouts
Mindfulness: Guided Meditation, Breathwork, Visual Meditations, Yoga Nidra, Sound Healing

CONNECT WHEREVER 

From the comfort of your living room to a hotel room across the globe, we put your favorite classes for mind and body at your fingertips — available on phone, tablet, and web. No Wi-Fi? Download classes offline and take your practice on the go.

- Get a game plan for success with 24 Smart Start™, a multi-week fitness plan customized to you and your goals
 
- Go straight to working out with workouts picked for you daily that fit your goals, equipment and current location

- Add workouts and plans to your Favorites to keep your most-loved sessions on repeat
 
 
ACHIEVE YOUR RESULTS FASTER with Thousands of Workouts and Plans
 
- Explore in-club and at home workouts from 24 Hour Fitness and trusted partners like LES MILLS®, Zumba®, Kettlebell Kings™ and more
  
- Adapt Smart Workouts to fit your needs in the moment: skip or swap out exercises, change the intensity, or add or remove equipment for the perfect fit
 
- Get expert coaching with audio-guided cardio workouts with options available for treadmill, elliptical, bike, rower and more
 
- Explore multi-week fitness plans for every goal and personalize them to fit your schedule
 
 
STAY ON TRACK TO RESULTS with Scheduling and Reminders
 
- Allow access to your mobile calendar, so you can plan out your week and add workouts and classes
 
- Receive alerts and reminders about your reserved classes, workouts and training sessions, so you never miss the best part of your day
 
 
MEASURE YOUR PROGRESS with Performance and Goal Tracking
 
- Apple Health integration – The 24GO app can send your workout data (Active Energy, Heart Rate, and Workouts) to Apple Health, so they count towards your Activity Rings. It can also read data from Apple Health (Date of Birth, Height, Weight and Sex) and use this data to recommend 24GO workouts.
 
- Fitbit integration - Connect your Fitbit account and your 24GO workouts will count towards your goals in Fitbit
 
- Heart Rate Monitor integration - Add your Bluetooth 4.0 capable device and view HR inside your workout
 
- Download to your Apple Watch to track your performance during your 24GO workouts

- Earn badges as you work out, check into the club and log activity to celebrate your achievements
 
 
GET THE MOST FROM YOUR 24 HOUR FITNESS® MEMBERSHIP
 
- Find 24 Hour Fitness® clubs, coaches and classes near you when you enable location services
 
- Use the QR code in the app or on your Apple Watch for quick and easy touch-free club check-in
 
- Reserve your favorite studio classes, add them to your mobile calendar, set reminders and get real-time updates*
 
- Add your 24 Hour Fitness® coach to your account for extra accountability and personalized support
 
 
The 24GO app is free to download and use. Messaging and data rates may apply. *Not all features are available to all 24 Hour Fitness® members.
 
 
The 24GO Privacy Policy is here: https://www.24hourfitness.com/company/policies/privacy/privacy_policy.html

apps.title: FlexIt - Fitness
apps.description:
FlexIt is the most convenient and easy-to-use way to access fitness, Wherever, Whenever. Train virtually with live personal trainers or visit one of thousands of partner gyms.  Work out from home, the gym, or anywhere - all at affordable rates.
 
HOW DOES FLEXIT WORK?
 
FlexIt has two offerings that enable seamless access to personalized and flexible fitness.
 
Virtual Personal Training (VPT) is the most personalized, private, and custom digital fitness experience. VPT lets you train live with expert trainers from trusted brands from anywhere in the world.
 
Plus, FlexIt gives you flexible, pay-as-you-go access to thousands of fitness facilities across the United States. Check-in by scanning the QR code at the front desk and enter the gym without worrying about tours, day passes, or paperwork.
 
HOW DOES VIRTUAL PERSONAL TRAINING WORK?
 
Training virtually with a personal trainer is incredibly simple. Using FlexIt’s video technology, you can take personalized, 1-on-1 training sessions with live trainers. Sessions can be taken from within the FlexIt app or from FlexIt’s website.
 
Each session is customized specifically for you by your trainer so it’s perfect for your fitness level and goals.
 
IS VIRTUAL PERSONAL TRAINING EFFECTIVE?
 
FlexIt VPT has been shown to be extremely effective in helping users build and maintain healthy habits. 88% of users surveyed reported that VPT is significantly more effective than pre-recorded workouts.  73% preferred it to an in-person personal training session. FlexIt VPT has been featured on ABC News, The Today Show, and Men’s Journal.
 
WHO ARE THE FLEXIT TRAINERS?
 
FlexIt works with some of the biggest brands in fitness to offer you access to an unprecedented variety of trainers and fitness styles. By working out with FlexIt, you can be sure you’re getting the best. Our trainers specialize in all fitness styles including strength training, cardio, yoga, and pilates.  Plus, get comprehensive health support like diet and nutrition guidance, meditation, and pre / post natal care.
 
HOW DOES FLEXIT’S FLEXIBLE GYM ACCESS WORK?
 
Visiting a FlexIt gym is seamless, flexible, and paper-free with no additional waiver or FlexIt membership required. Here’s how it works:
 
 - Search for gym or fitness studios on the FlexIt app.
 - Once you arrive at a gym, use the app to scan the QR mount at the front desk to check-in: no waiver required.
 - When you’re ready to leave, simply check out and pay only for the time you were there.

apps.title: Butt Workout: Fitness at Home
apps.description:
Welcome to Butt Workout by 7M, your ultimate personal trainer for shaping, toning, and strengthening your glutes, right in your pocket. Never miss out on achieving your fitness goals, regardless of how busy your schedule is!
Our app is purpose-built with quick, yet powerful routines meticulously designed to give you the best results in the least amount of time. Whether you're at home, work, or on the go, Butt Workout by 7M is your perfect companion toward a fitter, healthier you.
What sets us apart?
Effective Workouts: Our workouts are created by certified fitness professionals to ensure you maximize each session. Get ready for a mix of squats, lunges, deadlifts, bridges, and more — all scientifically optimized to shape and tone your glutes.
Personalized Programs: Tailored to your fitness level and goals, our app adjusts workout routines, making each session perfect for you. It's like having a personal trainer always ready at your service.
User-Friendly Interface: The design is intuitive and easy to navigate. Set workout reminders, track your progress, and view your workout history effortlessly.
Workout Anywhere: Our workouts are designed for any setting — home, hotel room, or even the office. Get fit anytime, anywhere.
Progress Tracking: Visualize your journey with the app's in-built progress tracker. See your achievements, celebrate victories, and stay motivated as you inch closer to your goals.
Educational Content: Along with our top-notch workouts, the app offers fitness tips, advice, and articles to help you understand the "why" behind each routine.
Note: This app is developed for informational purposes only. You should always consult your physician or doctor before starting any new fitness program.
This app integrates with the Apple Health app.
Terms of Use: https://www.workoutinc.net/terms-of-use
Privacy Policy: https://www.workoutinc.net/privacy-policy

apps.description:
Fitness & Workout helps you achieve your personal wellness objectives by building personalized workout plans.

Get your smart fitness plan based on your personal goals and focused on your problem areas. Workout plans are created and curated by our world class fitness coaches. Fitness & Workout by Get In Shape provides short and easy guided workouts and training sessions from only 6 minutes per day. Share your results and get feedback from users from all around the world.

Looking for a proven workout plan? Join one of 3 Masterclass programs designed and used by the Get In Shape certified coaches:
• Booty Builder
• Super Strength
• 6 Week Abs

What will happen after thirty days of exercise? You'll finally achieve these goals:
• Bikini beach body
• Toned arms
• Flat tummy
• Peachy butt
• Skinny thighs
• Sculpted abs
• Lose weight

FEATURES:
- hundred of exercises carefully created for you
- video instructions for all the routines
- view your workout history to track the progress you achieved

Information about the auto-renewal of subscription:
- 1 week for $7.99 with a 3-day free trial period
- 1 week for $7.99 without a trial period
- 1 month for $19.99 with a 3-day free trial period
- 6 months for $39.99 without a trial period

- Your payment will be charged to your iTunes Account as soon as you confirm your purchase.
- You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal from your Account Settings after the purchase.
- Your subscription will renew automatically, unless you turn off auto-renew at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
- The cost of renewal will be charged to your account in the 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.
- When canceling a subscription, your subscription will stay active until the end of the period. Auto-renewal will be disabled, but the current subscription will not be refunded.
- Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when purchasing a subscription.

apps.title: Alive by Whitney Simmons
apps.description:
It’s a beautiful day to be Alive!

Placing your physical and mental wellness at the forefront, Alive was designed to offer a safe and empowering space for women to build strength, confidence, and lifelong habits.

Created by fitness experts, Alive meets you exactly where you are in your journey and guides you toward becoming your strongest, most confident self from the inside and out

Alive App Features
- Simple, intuitive design focused on your workout experience
- 20+ guided programs to match your goals and fitness level
- 30-day mental & physical wellness challenges
- 200+ daily workouts to mix and match
- Beginner, Intermediate, and advance difficulty levels
- Select between gym and at-home equipment options

Meet the Trainers
- Whitney Simmons - Leads with a well rounded strength training, focused to help maximize strength utilizing progressive overload, and creating a balanced physique.
- Madeleine Abeid - Certified classic mat Pilates instructor with experience in sculpt & fusion practice. Bringing mat pilates to Alive in a follow along format.
- Libby Christensen - Brings your strength to the next level by utilizing progressive overload training adaptions with an emphasis on compound movements
- Marissa McNamara - Uses her power training systems to build maximum strength, placing an emphasis on compound movements.
- Felicia Keathley - Primarily focuses to help you master essential and foundational exercises. Also known for her pregnancy and postpartum programing.

Programs
Choose from over 20 expert-designed programs. Each program guides you through a structured schedule across several week so you can focus less on planning and more on showing up.

Challenges
Our 30-day challenges are where fitness and mindfulness meet with daily journal prompts, mobility sessions, and habits to support your mental and physical well-being.

Daily Workouts
Don’t want a set program? Choose from 200+ daily workouts across categories like HIIT, core, pull, push, and more. Perfect for mixing things up or staying on track when life gets busy.

Your Journey
The path to a fit, healthy life is a journey, not an overnight process. Stay motivated by logging weight, photos, and completed workouts. See your growth over time and earn achievements along the way. Sync with Apple Health for a complete view of your activity.

Alive Premium
Alive is free to download with Premium plans (Monthly or Annual), both with a 7-day free trial. Premium unlocks full access to all programs, challenges, and daily workouts.

Your subscription will be charged to your Apple account and will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the current period ends. 

You may manage your subscriptions and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings after the purchase. After purchase, refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term. You agree to our Privacy Policy and Terms & Conditions by downloading and subscribing to Alive Premium.

https://aliveapp.co/terms
https://aliveapp.co/privacy

General bug fixes and performance updates.

NEED HELP?
Email us at support@aliveapp.co

apps.title: iCardio Workout Tracker
apps.description:
iCardio – The Ultimate Heart Rate Training and Tracking App with Apple Watch and Apple Health Integration!

iCardio is your all-in-one solution for heart rate training and heart rate tracking, now featuring integrated YouTube workout videos! Whether you're working out indoors or outdoors, accessing video classes and tutorials, iCardio helps you visualize your efforts and achieve your fitness goals.

Why Choose iCardio?

iCardio is the perfect workout and cardio fitness tracker for any environment. With hundreds of fresh YouTube workout videos, you can get in the best shape of your life. Our app brings your heart rate and training zones to life, guiding you through effective workouts to maximize your training.

Comprehensive Tracking

Track everything you need to maintain a healthy heart, from daily steps and general activity to intense gym sessions, runs, or bike rides. With personalized Fitness Assessments, you can customize your heart rate and power zones. Our Routes & Routines feature takes your workouts to the next level by allowing you to create and compare personal routines over time.

Outstanding Features

* Personalized Voice Coaching: Get tailored coaching to enhance your workouts.
* LiveTracking: Let friends and family follow your progress in real-time.
* Goal Setting: Set and achieve your fitness goals with ease.
* Seamless Integration

iCardio seamlessly integrates with Apple Health and Apple Watch, as well as other heart rate monitors like Polar, Wahoo, Scosche, Viiiiva, POWR LABS, CooSpo, OrangeTheory, Garmin, and Moofit. Whether you use a Power Watts Meter, cadence sensor, or a Peloton® bike, iCardio provides a comprehensive solution for all your training needs.

Free Features

* Extensive library of YouTube workouts
* GPS routes for outdoor workouts
* Customizable voice coaching
* Heart rate monitor tracking and training
* Health metrics tracking: weight, blood pressure, resting pulse, and sleep
* Web sync for easy access and storage

Compatibility:

* Apple Health
* Garmin
* Fitbit

Share Your Workouts:

* Apple Health
* Strava
* MyFitnessPal
* TrainingPeaks

Subscriptions

STAR Membership – Yearly subscription for $29.99 USD or $4.99 per month.

* Advanced heart rate tracking and zone support with Apple Watch or compatible heart rate monitor (Bluetooth Smart)
* Real-time heart rate charts and zone analysis
* Speed and cadence sensor support
* Fitness assessments
* Custom workout Routes & Routines
* LiveTracking for real-time progress sharing
* Group creation for data sharing with friends
* Deeper insights through activity comparison
* Ad-free experience and more

Subscription Details

Payments are charged to your iTunes Account upon purchase confirmation. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Renewal charges occur within 24 hours before the end of the current period, at $29.99 per year or $4.99 per month. Unused portions of free trial periods are forfeited upon subscription purchase.

apps.title: Lose Belly Fat - Abs Workout
apps.description:
Congratulations on finding the "Lose Belly Fat" app! This powerful tool has helped thousands of people achieve their goal of a flat stomach. With just a few minutes a day, you can complete a 30-day abs workout program that is suitable for all fitness levels. Best of all, you can do these exercises in the comfort of your own home or anywhere you like.

Our app reveals the secrets to reducing calories naturally in your day-to-day life, allowing you to burn belly fat and achieve your desired flat stomach. We provide the best ab exercises that will help you build a strong core and melt away belly fat effectively.

Features:
1. Best Ab Exercises: Our app offers a wide range of exercises that target your abdominal muscles and promote belly fat loss. Get ready to experience the most effective belly fat loss program available.
2. 30-Day Home Workout: In just 10 minutes a day, without the need for any equipment, you can follow our professionally designed workout routines. These routines are guided by certified fitness coaches and will transform your abs in just 30 days.
3. Women Workout - Female Fitness: Our app is perfect for women who desire a toned and sexy flat stomach. The exercises provided are highly effective for women.
4. Weight Loss Fast: All the exercises in our app are free and designed to burn belly fat and tone your abs at home. You'll experience rapid fat burning and achieve your weight loss goals quickly.
5. Men Workout: Our app is not only suitable for women but also offers effective exercises for men. In just 30 days, men will notice a significant change in their bodies.
6. Fitness Coach at Home: All the programs in our app have been developed by certified fitness trainers. You don't need any gym equipment to perform your abs workout. Use our app anytime, anywhere, and let it guide you to your fitness goals.

This app is integrated with HealthKit, so you can easily track your calories burned by syncing the data to the Health App. Simply turn on the "Apple Health" option and keep your progress in check.

Download the "Lose Belly Fat" app now and start your journey towards a stronger, fitter body! Say goodbye to belly fat and hello to a healthier you. Get ready to transform your abs and achieve the flat stomach you've always wanted.

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING & TERMS
Lose Belly Fat app is free to download and use. Should you choose to upgrade to the premium version, we offer an auto-renewing subscription option.
Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase
• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period
• Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal
• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase
• Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable.
Read our full Privacy Policy at https://takalogy.com/privacy-policy/
For our full terms of use, please visit: https://takalogy.com/terms-and-conditions-of-use/

apps.title: Fitness Verv: Daily Exercise
apps.description:
If you’ve ever wondered how to get fit and healthy with minimal effort, look no further. Verv is your all-in-one solution for that.

It features four building blocks – physical activity, nutrition, sleep and mindfulness – all defined by simplicity, effectiveness and personalization.

Choose what you like from an extensive library of solutions for a healthier lifestyle:


WIDE RANGE OF FITNESS WORKOUTS

• Large variety of at-home exercises for weight loss
• Body-toning fitness programs for all trouble zones
• Collection of workouts with resistance bands
• Unique 30-day fitness challenges to keep your motivation high


RUNNING & WALKING SESSIONS

• A wide range of training programs for weight loss and body tone
• Interval trainings with audio instructions
• Detailed stats for progress tracking
• Custom-made plans made for your goals


MEAL PLANS FOR EVERY TASTE

• Delicious recipes with prep time and number of calories
• Keto and intermittent fasting plans
• Vegan and vegetarian plans
• Meal plan collections to benefit your training


MEDITATION & YOGA PRACTICES

• 270+ guided meditations & short practices
• Step-by-step meditation courses
• 5-min singles for stress relief
• Programs for better sleep, anxiety-relief, and more


ENERGETIC DANCE TUTORIALS

• Guided dance workouts for all levels
• Learn from the celebrity choreographer
• Routines that give you tone and burn calories


SOUNDS FOR YOGA PRACTICE AND RELAXATION

• Peaceful music to keep you focused on your mind and body during yoga sessions
• Calming melodies to help you unwind
• Sleep Stories and ASMR so you can drift off and sleep peacefully

Enjoy workouts, yoga practices, meal plans, meditations, running and walking sessions separately or as a combination of activities. One way or the other, take the most out of your experience.

You can allow Verv access to Apple Health to sync your weight, height, heart rate, running and walking distance, active energy, and workout data.


INFO ABOUT USING THE APP AND REGARDING THE SUBSCRIPTION TERMS OF USE AND SUBSCRIPTION DETAILS

The upgrade to Premium provides access to the variety of training plans, collections, singles, meditations and sounds, audio coaches, and turns the advertisements off. You can choose from monthly, quarterly or annual subscriptions, price varies by location.

- Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase
- Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period
- Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal
- Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase
- Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable.


Privacy Policy: https://verv.com/vervapp-ios-privacy-policy/
Terms of Use: https://verv.com/vervapp-ios-terms-and-conditions-of-use/


Note: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.
This app is developed for informational purposes only. You must always consult your physician or doctor before starting any fitness program. Results can vary.


Follow us!
Facebook: https://facebook.com/Verv/
Twitter: @verv_inc
Instagram: @verv

apps.title: Jillian Michaels | Fitness App
apps.description:
Subscribe to Jillian Michaels | The Fitness App and get beach body ready with the most comprehensive customizable fitness, nutrition, and mindfulness features all on one seamless platform.

Try a 7-day trial of Premium Access!

PERSONALIZED FITNESS PLANNER

Over 1000 + workout exercises in HD video to stream on your phone, tablet, or TV! The Fitness App offers personalized workout programs for any fitness level from beginner workouts to advanced! Meet any goal from weight loss to toning up trouble areas! Train with at home workouts, in the gym, exercise outside, or choose audio only workouts!

The Fitness App includes all your favorite workouts: yoga, HIIT, kickboxing, walking & running programs including 5K & 10k training with GPS tracker, pre & postnatal options, ab workouts, butt workouts & more!

The premium subscription also has a Workout Generator to build unique targeted workouts with 10, 20, 30 or 45 minute options to create customized ab workout, leg workout, butt workout, or total body workout just for you!

• Adjust workout intensity
• Select fitness goal
• Select Available Fitness Equipment
• Select fitness preferences
• Select workout length
• Swap and ban exercises
• Adjust transition time between exercises
• Play your own music during workout
• Let Beat Sync adjust the beat of music to pace of workout
• Siri shortcuts to open, pause, stop workouts
• Apple Watch for Heart rate tracking
• Apple Rings and activity integration
• Integrates with Apple Health

DVD WORKOUT LIBRARY

Plus, subscribers have access to stream Jillian's DVD workout library including the full Bodyshred and Body Revolution programs.

CUSTOMIZED MEAL PLANNER

Try the Advanced Meal Planner!

The Fitness App is your personal diet coach with the Advanced Meal Planner system that helps you reach your weight loss goals or maintain a healthy lifestyle. Beyond just planning your own meals, the Advanced Meal Planner System features tools to help plan meals for the whole family!

• Meal Plans for every preference: Omnivore, Vegan, Vegetarian, Paleo & Gluten Free, Pescatarian, Keto, 5 Minute Meals and more!
• Hundreds of quick delicious nutritious recipes
• Ban ingredients
• Grocery lists
• Dynamically adjust recipes for weight loss, maintenance, or muscle gain
• Pick the meals and days to eat on or off plan
• Dynamically adjust number of servings in a recipe
• Options for batch cooking so you can plan to eat delicious leftovers
• Mark favorite recipes

MINDFULNESS

Sleep better. Stress less with mindfulness exercises & meditations ranging from sleep to stress management. Relax & unwind with nature sounds, motivational practices, body scans, mindful eating meditations & more.

TRACKING

Track your progress: weight, calories, activity, workout history and more. You can even take weekly side by side progress pics with the selfie photo tracker and share data with My Fitness Pal.

SUPPORT

Get daily custom health & fitness tips from Jillian to help you stay on track!

Download now & start your 7-day trial of premium access to personalized workout programs, meal plans, meditations & mindfulness, community, support, and more.

SUBSCRIPTION & PRICING TERMS

We offer 3 premium subscription plans: Monthly (1 month), Quarterly (3 months), Annual (12 months). Unless canceled or auto-renew is turned off 24-hours before the end of subscription term or the 7-day trial period, you will be billed automatically based on your chosen subscription plan at the end of the free trial or on your subscription renewal date.

Manage your subscription and disable auto-renewal in your Account Settings after purchase or trial start. Read full Terms of Service and Privacy Policy at: https://www.jillianmichaels.com/policies/terms

• Bug fixes and UI/UX improvements

apps.title: atZone: Home Workout Partner
apps.description:
Now you can get a complete workout at home that’s as immersive as it is inspiring, whether you love a great run, a smooth elliptical workout, an exhilarating ride, strength training or a little bit of everything. With Horizon Fitness equipment featuring @Zone, you can take on workouts personalized to your unique goals, redefine your body with HIIT, access on-demand classes, take on guided strength training with our advanced motion tracking system or race through exotic virtual journeys. You can even sync your workout data to third-party apps, connect wearables and chart your progress against the top @Zone users worldwide. Download the app today, and make sure your next workout is in the zone. 

MOVE YOUR WAY
Whether you’re passionate about running, cycling, strength training or cross-training, @Zone has you covered. With support for multiple workout formats, you can keep your routine exciting and perfectly tailored to your fitness goals.

GET RESULTS YOU CAN SEE IN THE MIRROR
Count on transformative results with scientifically validated Sprint 8 HIIT. Sprint 8 uses high-intensity interval training to stimulate a natural human growth hormone, burning fat and building muscle in ways fads can’t. Best of all, anyone can fit the short, 20-minute workouts into their schedule, and they can be done right in your home on your treadmill, indoor cycle, exercise bike or elliptical.

EXPERIENCE THE STUDIO AT HOME
With a range of on-demand fitness classes and motivating trainers at your fingertips, you’ll always be able to access an inspiring studio experience right for your goals and schedule, right in your home. No matter how you like to get your heart pumping, you’ll discover workouts that pair perfectly with your home cardio and strength equipment. 

EXPLORE THE WORLD AT HOME
Our Virtual Active exercise program transports your home workout to exotic locales all over the world. Shot on location by professional film crews, the HD footage speeds up or slows down to match your workout, and incline varies to match the terrain, making you feel like you’re really there. You can even race against your own best performances, motivating you to beat your own avatar to the finish line. 

MEET YOUR NEW COACH
Get personalized training plans designed around your specific objectives — be it improving heart health, burning calories or building muscle — with our versatile and goal-oriented training assistant. With built-in programs for tracking time, distance, calories and heart rate, @Zone makes sure you’re always on the path to success.
CAPTURE EVERY REP & SET
Our unique motion tracking system detects the position of your skeleton for guided strength training workouts. Not only will @Zone help you refine your form on a wide variety of exercises for better results, it will also keep track of your reps and sets when using dumbbells and kettlebells for a more streamlined experience. 


STAY ON TRACK FOR YOUR GOALS
A home workout history feature consolidates exercise data and lets you review your fitness progress from workout to workout and by weeks, months and years. You can even access the worldwide leaderboard to see how your performance compares to the top users of @Zone. 

CONNECT & SYNC
If you’re using a third-party app like Apple Health, Fitbit or others to exercise, @Zone will automatically sync your workout data across platforms and devices so you can see everything in one place. You can even connect your smart watch to put complete control of strength workouts on your wrist.

This application is for people who want to exercise and get back into shape, without complicated movements, exercises or programs that require equipment. You can get back into shape at your own pace and at home. Getting back into shape, building muscle, losing weight and keeping your balance is now easier and more effective thanks to FizzUp
 
The app is free to download and also offers premium programs to explore other health and training areas, as well as programs to get you started with yoga training and reconnect with yourself through our guided meditations.

apps.title: Gravity Fit: Super Fat Burning
apps.description:
Ready to transform your body with a flat belly, lean legs, and toned glutes? Look no further than Gravity Fit! Take your pick from workouts that target your trouble zones or follow a pre-designed program customized just for you, helping you achieve the results you desire.

Don't just take our word for it – check out these success stories from our satisfied users:

"Gravity Fit's training program deserves a huge shoutout! I lost 3 kg in a month without making any changes to my diet. Thank you!" – Alejandra, Mexico, July 2022

"I'll admit it, I'm a bit lazy when it comes to exercise. But Gravity Fit's simple and short training sessions caught my attention. They started off easy, but gradually increased in intensity. Even with the added challenge, the workouts didn't take up much time. I'm already seeing results and motivated to keep going!" – Susan, Australia, November 2022

With Gravity Fit, we've got everything you need to turn regular workouts into a habit and smash your fitness goals. The best part? You can exercise whenever and wherever you want, without any equipment!

Check out what we offer:

TAILORED PROGRAMS

Our smart algorithm considers your goals, gender, age, height, weight, and health limitations to select the perfect program. It adjusts the plan based on your progress, ensuring each day brings something new. We've also handpicked over 200 short workouts for abs & core, glutes, arms, chest, and more.

EXERCISE ANYTIME, ANYWHERE

Whether you have 5 minutes or 45 minutes to spare, we've got a workout to fit your schedule. No need to invest in expensive equipment – start training anytime, anywhere. Whether it's at home or at the gym, the choice is yours.

EXPERTLY DESIGNED WORKOUTS

All our programs are crafted by certified fitness trainers, based on the scientifically proven Afterburn effect. The exercises and training loads are carefully chosen to keep your body burning calories even up to 30 hours after your workout.

SAFETY FIRST

We understand that beginners can be prone to injuries, so we prioritize your safety. Each exercise comes with detailed voice and video instructions in high definition. If you've had past injuries, simply let us know, and we'll personalize your program accordingly.

Additional features to elevate your training experience:

– Offline Mode: No internet? No problem. Download workouts and exercise offline.
– Personalized Music: Enjoy music that adapts to your workout pace and your preferences.
– Apple Watch Compatibility: Control your workout seamlessly from your wrist.
– 24/7 Coach Support: Have questions? Our certified trainers are here to assist you around the clock.
– Progress Tracking: Sync with Apple Health to record your workout information and import data about your weight and body parameters.

Attention: Make sure to consult your doctor about any health limitations before beginning an exercise program.

SUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION

– Subscribe for unlimited access to all of our workouts.
– Choose from weekly, monthly, 6 month or 12 month plans*.
– Payment is easy using your iTunes account.
– Your incredible program will automatically renew to keep you in shape.
– Should your needs change, you can always manage your subscription preferences in iTunes Account Settings.

*The price is equivalent to the value in “Apple’s App Store Matrix,” determined according to the subscription price in $USD.

Privacy Policy: https://www.gravityhome.fit/privacy
Terms of Use: https://www.gravityhome.fit/terms

apps.title: StepBet: Walk, Get Active, Win
apps.description:
Become more active and earn money doing it! Receive personalized Step Goals based on your activity/exercise tracker history, and bet money on yourself during weekly health-focused games where you’ll be encouraged to walk and exercise to meet your personalized step targets.

How it works: 

- Download the StepBet app.
- Select your step source (Apple Health, Apple Watch, Fitbit, and Garmin) to get your custom fitness goals.
- Find a game and place a bet into the game’s pot to officially join. 
- Walk, exercise, and stay active to hit your fitness goals every week of the game.
- Win, and split the pot with other winners to recoup your bet and then some!

By committing real money, engaging in the social aspect of our games, and interacting with our one-of-a-kind customer support team, you’ll find unparalleled motivation in reaching your health and fitness goals. 

Try it risk-free! Cancel any time during the first week for a full refund.

apps.title: PNCH: Boxing and Fitness
apps.description:
PNCH offers you a personal training plan to make sure you reach your fitness goals (weight loss, body tone, …). Everything you need for a workout is available on the app.

Each workout is fully customized for your needs and can help with any of the following:

- Weight Loss 
- Body Sculpt / Core Conditioning 
- High-intensity interval training (HIIT) 
- Standalone Workouts 

NO EQUIPMENT NEEDED
You get the convenience of working out on your own schedule. No more driving to and from the gym or waiting for your turn on the equipment. Everything you need for a workout is available on the app.

PERSONAL 4-WEEK PLAN
Answer a few simple questions to build your routine, based on your goals, schedule and fitness level. Choose how often you like to work out and get a four-week training plan, adapted to your specific requirements. 

100+ BODYWEIGHT EXERCISES
Do you ever get bored doing the same workouts over and over? With PNCH, you’ll get instant access to a wide variety of exercises to keep you motivated. 

- Choose from 100+ exercises for any gender, goal or fitness level
- Target your upper body, ABS or lower body
- Get a wide variety of workouts, from boxing to stretching
- Challenge yourself to 5-40 minutes, depending on your schedule and fitness level 

EASY-TO-FOLLOW INSTRUCTIONS
HD videos provide demonstrations by our trainers and detailed, easy-to-follow instructions. We’ve also included a handy Voice Coach feature for extra support during workouts!

Get the freedom, flexibility, and privacy to achieve your fitness goals. Follow your four-week fitness plan to get real results without bulky gym equipment or pricey memberships. Download PNCH and say hi to a healthier, fitter you!

SUBSCRIPTION & TERMS
PNCH is free to download. Access your personal training plan and full standalone workouts and exercises require an active subscription, available on a monthly or yearly basis. Customers who choose a monthly subscription are eligible for a free 7-day trial period. Yearly subscriptions billed the total annual fee from the purchase date. Monthly subscription users billed per month.

Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. The account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, at the cost of the chosen package. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when subscribing to a non-trial plan. 
Read our full Terms of Service and our Privacy Policy at https://pnch.app/terms-conditions

Note: This app is developed for informational purposes only. You must always consult your physician or doctor before starting any training program. Results can vary.

apps.title: Fit4Me: Workout & Weight Loss
apps.description:
Fit4Me: Workout & Weight Loss - Your Personalized Fitness Companion!

Are you ready to embark on a fitness journey tailored just for you? Look no further than Fit4Me, your go-to fitness app that creates personalized and unique programs designed to help you achieve your health and fitness goals. With a wide range of features and tools, Fit4Me is your one-stop solution for a healthier and more active lifestyle.

• Workout Planner & Tracker:
Fit4Me empowers you to plan and track your daily workouts with ease. Whether you prefer hitting the gym, practicing yoga, or exercising at home, our app has you covered. Get personalized workout plans that adapt to your fitness level and goals.

• Nutrition Counter:
Monitor your daily food intake effortlessly with our nutrition counter. Keep tabs on your calorie consumption and make informed choices to support your fitness journey. Fit4Me helps you maintain a balanced diet tailored to your needs.

• Fasting Scheduler:
Interested in intermittent fasting? Fit4Me offers a fasting scheduler to help you optimize your eating patterns. Customize your fasting schedule and track your progress to reap the benefits of this popular health trend.

• Hydration Tracker:
Staying hydrated is crucial for your overall well-being. Fit4Me reminds you to drink water throughout the day and tracks your water intake to ensure you stay properly hydrated.

• Daily Planner:
Plan your daily activities and set reminders to stay on track with your fitness goals. Fit4Me's daily planner keeps you organized and motivated, helping you build healthy habits.

• Fitness Coach:
Get access to expert guidance and coaching right at your fingertips. Fit4Me connects you with certified fitness coaches who can provide personalized advice and support to help you reach your objectives.

• Progress Tracking:
Track your progress with detailed statistics and charts. See how your workouts, nutrition, and fasting schedules are impacting your body, and adjust your plans accordingly.

• Profile:
Create a personal profile to store your fitness data and achievements. Connect with a community of like-minded individuals and share your journey to inspire and motivate others.

Fit4Me is not just another fitness app; it's your partner on the path to a healthier, fitter you. Our commitment to providing personalized programs and expert guidance sets us apart. Whether you're a fitness enthusiast or a beginner, Fit4Me is designed to meet your unique needs and support your health and wellness journey.

Fit4Me is a subscription-based app that offers personalized fitness and meal plans, fasting schedules, a water intake tracker, and detailed progress statistics. In addition to custom-tailored programs, Fit4Me provides a variety of specialized workout routines, including stretching sessions, Wall Pilates, Chair Yoga, and targeted workouts for different muscle groups. To unlock all these premium features, an active subscription is mandatory.

Ready to take control of your health and fitness? Download Fit4Me now and start your personalized fitness journey today!

Privacy Policy - https://sites.google.com/view/fit4me-app/privacy-policy
Terms of Use - https://sites.google.com/view/fit4me-app/terms-of-use

On top of that, we’ve enhanced animations and visuals for a more polished feel, and fixed a few bugs to make everything run better.


Thanks for sticking with us - we hope you enjoy the latest version!

apps.description:
Sweat in 20 minutes or less with FitHer. Our smart exercise app provides your very own personalized workout plan based on your goals, level, and physical condition to achieve great results. Start a 30-day program designed by top coaches that's scientifically proven to help you lose weight faster. It’s time to hit your fitness goals with a complete exercise platform that’ll put you on the right track to seeing remarkable results.

Hit your daily workouts with workout videos made for everyone – no matter what stage you are at in your
fitness journey. Select a workout plan for different goals. Whether you are targeting specific muscles or
want a complete routine, FitHer has you covered. Blast fat with Full Body, tone your quads and hammies
with Hot Legs, or get a quick sweat in with 7-Minute Workout, there’s something for everyone.

Complement your transformation in the kitchen with different meal plans to choose from. With FitHer you
get to choose how you get your calories in. Keto? Veggie? Gluten-Free? We have it all. You can even
enjoy your very own water tracker to make sure you’re staying hydrated throughout the day and during
your workouts.

FitHer is your personal tool for meeting and exceeding your fitness goals. Download today!

FitHer Features

Weight Loss Workouts That Work For You
- Get a personalized workout plan and see the body of your dreams in just 30 days
- Discover workout plans designed by professional coaches
- Explore different difficulty levels – Beginner, Medium, and Active

Daily Workouts With In-Depth Tools
- Get in-depth guidance on each exercise with videos
- Track your weight loss transformation directly in-app
- Earn achievements after workouts and make your fitness journey fun
- Track your progress through your Apple Watch

Start Your Own Diet Plan
- Create a meal plan based on your dietary needs – keto, vegetarian, and gluten-free
- Get your macros in and make sure you’re on track to meeting your weight loss goals
- Abs are made in the kitchen. Support your workouts with healthy recipes to lose weight

Workout Plans
- Full body (This 4-week plan is designed to blast fat, boost metabolism, and build muscle)
- Hot Legs (A simple workout that helps slim and tone your legs)
- Arms & Breasts (The best workout plan to tone arms and lift breast)
- Gorgeous Butt (This 4-week workout challenge transforms your rear from every angle)
- Flat Stomach (Easy Workout to lose belly fat in just 30 days)
- 7-Minute Workout (Scientifically proven to keep you fit with 7 minutes of workout a day)
- HIIT Workout (High-intensity workout plan that will make you sweat)

SUBSCRIPTION DETAILS

Premium service gives access to advanced features of the app. Non-subscribed users will only be able to complete day 1 of the training program. You may need to subscribe to our premium service if you wish to continue your workouts.

• Payment is charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.
• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can turn off the auto-renew subscription from your device settings.
• Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.
• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase.
• Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription.

To manage your subscription or turn off auto-renewal on your iPhone:
1. Open the Settings app
2. Tap your name or Apple ID
3. Tap Subscriptions
4. Tap the subscription you want to manage
5. Use the options to manage your subscription

Whether you’re looking to stay cool while training for your next half-marathon, practicing with your team, or hiking outdoors, get all your workout essentials online from Under Armour. 
 
In the UA App, you can find:  
* Exclusive collections including Curry Brand, Project Rock. 
* New drop alerts that notify you when we release our latest sneakers, clothing, and accessories. 
* Tailored product recommendations to support your training and fitness goals. 
* Free shipping, returns, and exchanges. 
* Member-exclusive benefits and rewards when you join our UA Rewards program.

Whether you play basketball or baseball, or are a runner in training, get personalized recommendations for footwear and apparel so you can crush your next workout. We designed our performance apparel to withstand your training while keeping you comfortable and locked-in. This is go-to athletic gear—for men, women, boys, and girls—all right here. Still waiting for next summer to train your legs and butt? Start right now to feel the positive changes in your body after a few weeks, be proud of yourself!

Proper form during exercises is the most important aspect of sculpting toned legs and a tight butt. Usually the exercises need to target three major muscle groups - butt, thighs, and leg muscles.

Butt & Legs Workout offers you a new training method:  A 30-day systematic exercise plan - it's more effective but requires less equipment and has fewer restrictions.

You can easily do it at home or anywhere at any time, just 10 minutes each day. It’s more than just a private coach. It offers animations and video guidance for each exercise. By following our workout, you will notice a change in the shape of your butt and legs been in just a few short weeks.

Features
- On "Me" page, turn on the "Apple Health" switch to sync the information of your height, weight, calories to Apple Health
- No surprise and hidden charges
- Different workouts every day
- Increases exercise intensity step by step
- Coach tips in every exercise help you use the right form to get better results
- No need for equipment, workout with your body weight
- Track weight loss progress

apps.title: Virtuagym: Fitness & Workouts
apps.description:
Looking to lose weight, build muscle, enhance flexibility, or reduce stress? Virtuagym Fitness supports your journey at home, outdoors or in the gym. Designed for beginners and enthusiasts, our AI Coach creates personalized plans from over 5,000 3D exercises. Stream video workouts like HIIT, cardio, and yoga to your TV, and begin with ease.
 
PERSONALIZED WORKOUTS BY AI COACH
Embrace the power of customized fitness with AI Coach. Our library of over 5,000 3D exercises caters to diverse needs, from quick, equipment-free routines to targeted strength and weight loss workouts. Whether you're a beginner or an enthusiast, our app ensures your workout  is tailored just for you.

WORK OUT ANYTIME, ANYWHERE 
Your living room, your fitness studio. Our video library offers HIIT, Cardio, Strength Training, Pilates, and Yoga. Stream directly to your TV or mobile device anywhere.

VISUALIZE PROGRESS, ACHIEVE MORE 
Track your fitness journey with our Progress Tracker. Monitor calories burned, exercise duration, distance, and more. Integrated with Neo Health scales and wearables, track your health comprehensively.

EFFECTIVE WORKOUTS FOR EVERYONE
Enjoy safe, effective exercise routines with our 3D-animated personal trainer. Get detailed instructions for every fitness level.

EFFORTLESS FITNESS PLANNING
Easily plan and manage your fitness activities with our calendar. Schedule workouts, track your heart rate, and log progress, keeping your fitness routine organized and focused.

COMPLEMENTARY FOOD APP
Explore our food database and track nutrition tailored to your diet. Whether it’s high-protein or low-carb, get a holistic view of your eating habits for a healthier you.

HABIT TRACKER
Track daily routines with our simple habit tracker. Maintain consistency with streaks and stay on top of your goals. Ideal for cultivating healthy habits and achieving personal growth.

MINDFULNESS FOR A BALANCED LIFE
Integrate mindfulness and meditation into your life with our audio and video sessions. These practices are key for anyone looking to reduce stress and find mental balance, perfectly complementing your physical health efforts.

FULL APP EXPERIENCE 
Subscribe to PRO membership to access all the PRO features and content. Your subscription will automatically renew, and your account will be charged for the same amount as your current subscription fee 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, unless auto-renew is disabled at least 24 hours before. Manage or turn off auto-renewal in your Account Settings after purchase.

Terms of Use: 
https://support.virtuagym.com/s/terms-of-use

apps.title: Personal Trainer: Gravl
apps.description:
Build muscle, increase your strength, or get lean with Gravl. Whether you are at home in the gym or outside, Gravls training algorithm will provide you with a personalized workout designed to help you reach your fitness goals.

A new generation of fitness algorithm

Unlike existing fitness apps, Gravls Algorithm doesn't just assemble random workouts. Our technology looks at your unique attributes (gender, weight, age, training level) and studies your workout patterns to evolve around your schedule, goals, equipment, and place of training.

As you train more Gravl gets better. Your training plan will maximize your progress by adjusting intensity, volume, and weight for each session. The outcome is a balanced effective workout every time.

Optimal exercises

Not all exercises are created equal and Gravl knows this. We believe that mastering the most effective exercises is more important than having different exercises every time. We balance optimal movements and variation so that your exercises are diverse and challenging. 

For beginners, or seasoned gym-goers looking for new workouts, we have over 300 trainer-led videos so you can always add new movements with confidence.

Track your progress

Gravls Strength Score makes measuring your strength and progress straightforward. We calculate this based on 8 different subscores and millions of data points across people of your same age gender body weight and fitness experience.

Customization

You can let Gravl lead the way 100% or set up your own custom workout settings. You have the power to change your fitness goal, workout variety level, muscle split, duration, equipment, and more!

Coach Support

Get support from our coaches, whether you need tips to make the most of our app or workout advice, just message us in-app at any time.

Apple Health. 

Easily track your workouts and Calories burned with our Apple Health integration

Why Gravl?

Gravl combines leading fitness research, input from certified personal trainers, and constant feedback from our community to deliver a solution that is effective, affordable, and practical. 

Privacy: https://gravl.ai/privacy
Terms: https://gravl.ai/terms
Terms (EULA): https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/

apps.title: RockMyRun - Workout Music
apps.description:
ROCKMYRUN IS THE BEST WORKOUT MUSIC IN THE WORLD!

RockMyRun is music designed FOR running and working out. Our music is expertly selected and curated by professional DJs, not algorithms, to give you the optimal workout music experience. Compared to standard playlists, RockMyRun is proven to increase workout motivation and enjoyment by up to 35%!


LEGALLY LICENSED FOR CONSUMER USE ONLY. BUSINESS LICENSE AVAILABLE. 

If you intend to use RockMyRun at a place of business or are an independent fitness trainer you will need to get RMR with a commercial music license. Please contact brett@rockmygym.com or visit our business website at www.rockmygym.com for more information.


AWESOME FEATURES

► ADJUSTABLE BPM:
One-of-a-kind Body-Driven Music™ technology automatically adjusts music to sync with your steps or heart rate. You can also manually manipulate music to match your ideal BPM (beats per minute).

► DJ-CURATED MUSIC:
Our professional DJ’s curate specialized music to give you the best exercise experience for non-stop energy during your workout. (No more hitting skip!)

► NOT YOUR AVERAGE WORKOUT MUSIC:
RockMyRun is different from Spotify, Apple Music and Pandora Radio because all songs are specially selected and seamlessly blended together, creating a unique workout music experience unavailable in standard music apps. Our real DJs use only the best parts of your favorite songs to create the best music optimized for your run.

► RUN TRACKING:
Track your distance and pace while rocking out to the music you love, all in one app.

► TEMPO THAT BUILDS:
Stations build in BPM during your workout to help keep you going with the perfect exercise music at the perfect moment.

► PERSONALIZED SUGGESTIONS:
Get station suggestions that are constantly updated based on your listening preferences.

► ROBUST DISCOVERY OPTIONS:
Discover new music based on activity, mood, BPM, length, and genre. We’re proud to offer stations for Pop, Rock, Hip-hop, Rap, EDM, House, Dubstep, Drum & Bass, 70’s, 80’s, 90’s, Oldies, Christian, R&B, Latin, Reggae, Seasonal, Country, Alternative, Classical, and more.

► NOT JUST FOR RUNNING:
Use it as a gym playlist for the elliptical or treadmill, during a 10k run, with Couch to 5k, or while engaging in marathon training, crossfit, bootcamp, cycling, and so much more!

► WORKS WITH YOUR FAVORITE APPS:
RockMyRun functions seamlessly with running apps and tracking apps like Apple Health, Strava, Nike+, Runkeeper, MapMyFitness, Runtastic Endomondo, and more. They’ll do the tracking and we'll do the rocking while you’re training.


FEATURED IN

► NEW YORK TIMES:
“Music can be a great help to runners, but sometimes putting together a playlist can be a chore. Leave the running song selection up to RockMyRun.”

► LA TIMES:
“Great variety; it's easy to find something to your tastes. Choose from oldies, dubstep, hip-hop, country and a dozen other genres, then personalize it via preferred beats per minute, clean or explicit lyrics.”

► WALL STREET JOURNAL feature on WNBA MVP Elena Delle Donne:
“Ms. Delle Donne uses the app Rock My Run, which has a feature that matches the beat of songs to your pace.”

► GLAMOUR:
“These Pre-Made Music Mixes Will Change Everything”

► TODAY SHOW Co-Anchor, Natalie Morales:
“I am totally downloading this.”


HOW IT WORKS

Just for registering, you get a free trial and access to all premium content and features. Once the trial ends, you will automatically be upgraded to a premium account where you can sync unlimited running music to your body and listen to 1,000s of hours of music.
Questions? Email support@rockmyrun.com.


SERVICE DETAILS

► Length of subscription: Monthly or Yearly
► Price of subscription: Varies
► Payment will be charged to iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.
► Subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the scheduled renewal.
► The RockMyRun Terms of Service can be found here: https://www.rockmyrun.com/terms.php.

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References

apps.title: MadMuscles: Workouts & Diet
apps.description:
MadMuscles is a fitness app designed to help people gain muscle, lose weight, look hot and feel incredible. We make workouts accessible, effective and joyful by creating personalized workout plans tailored to each user’s needs and desires. No more excuses. It’s time to get the mad muscles you’ve always wanted!   

What makes MadMuscles effective?   

• Static and dynamic workouts for the best results 
Our workouts are designed for people with different fitness levels, lifestyles and goals: gain muscle, lose weight or get shredded. MadMuscles helps to work on different parts of the body – from stronger arms to toned legs, no muscle group is left behind. You can choose whether you want to workout at home or go to the gym – we’ve got you covered either way. 

• More than just regular strength training
We go way beyond classic workouts and keep things exciting. Introducing calisthenics and military workouts: push your limits and see if you’re up for the challenge. Or, if you prefer something more relaxed, try tai chi or chair yoga. Pick your new favorite workout, depending on your preferences and never get bored with the same routine.

• Video tutorials 
Don’t worry if you don’t know how to do a certain exercise – our high-quality professional video tutorials will show exactly how it’s done. 

• Exercise swap 
Don’t like the exercise in your workout plan? Swap it with the one you actually like. The app will choose an exercise for the same muscle group and of the same difficulty. 

• Achievements 
Get rewarded for your hard work. Achievements will make working out fun and will keep you motivated. 

• Sync with Apple health 
Sync MadMuscles with Apple health for better results. 

• Useful and fun challenges 
Make your body hot and your mind sharp. Develop healthy habits and discipline by trying our numerous challenges. You’ll never experience lack of motivation again – MadMuscles will not let you give up! 

• Personalized meal plans 
Nutrition is a key element in any body transformation process. Our meal plans are adjusted to your preferences and restrictions, with easy and quick recipes and a shopping list that will make cooking healthy and delicious meals easier. 

Privacy policy: https://madmuscles.com/privacy-policy
Terms of use: https://madmuscles.com/terms-of-service

apps.title: Fitify: Home Workout, AI Coach
apps.description:
Who needs a gym? Get in shape at home with workouts from FITIFY.

Fitify is your 100% personalized guide to lose weight, burn fat, build muscle strength. With over 900 exercises, your daily workout routines are always fresh, fun effective!

No gym required - you can only workout using the weight of your body (no equipment!). However, we are the only app out here also providing Workouts and Plans with fit tools, such as:

• Kettlebell
• TRX
• Bosu
• Exercise Ball
• Resistance Band
• Dumbbell
• Barbell
• Medicine Ball
• Foam Roller
• Pull-Up Bar

Fitify is your ultimate full body workout app to lose weight, burn fat, build muscle & strength. With over 900 exercises in the work out app, your daily workout routines are always fresh, fun & effective! Work out anywhere, anytime using any fit tool. No equipment required, but if you have one - take advantage of it!

What can we do for you?
• Personalized fitness plan - custom training plan based on your experience, goal, and time options. Each workout routine is created based on your personal fitness level to get you the best results.
• 15 minutes daily workouts
• over 850 bodyweight & fit tools exercises - so the workout is always fun, unique and effective
• 20+ prebuilt workouts - choose body part, type of training, and duration
• 15+ prebuilt recovery sessions - Stretching, Yoga, and Foam Rolling classes
• ability to build your own “Custom workout” from our huge exercise database
• works offline
• voice coach
• clear HD video demonstrations


FITNESS PLANS
• Weekly training plan full of Workout and Recovery sessions
• Workouts only take 15-25 minutes to complete.
• HIIT, Tabata, Strength Trainings, Cardio, and Recovery sessions with easy-to-follow video exercises.
• See history and track your awesome progress!

STANDALONE WORKOUTS
Whether you go bodyweight or use a tool like Kettlebell, you can choose to follow a plan or run any of our prebuilt workouts. Choose body part, type of training and duration. Simple as that, effective as hell!

CUSTOM WORKOUTS
Workout Routines blend your own workout from our beast database of over 900 exercises.

APPLE HEALTH
Connect Fitify to Apple Health and keep track of all your finished activities and burned calories.

Contact: support@gofitify.com
Terms of Use: https://gofitify.com/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://gofitify.com/privacy-policy.html

Thanks for reading to the end. Thanks for keeping yourself fit with us!

apps.description:
**#1 yoga app of 2023**——Apple 
**6000 million best choice**——Subscribers
**2019-2023 Best Yoga App**—Healthline

No.1 Yoga App Since 2012, loved by 60M+ people!

Daily Yoga - ALL IN ONE YOGA APP
-classic yoga
-chair yoga
-wall pilates
-somatic workout
-and more


Would you like to find both a yoga fitness pose video and meditations in one app?

Daily Yoga is the platform that provides health benefits for both your mind and body with multiple yoga poses, various guided yoga classes and weight loss yoga challenges.

Here are dozens of beginner-friendly yoga classes that are easy to learn and perform, including wall pilates, chair yoga, and sofa yoga. Start your day with a yoga workout that suits your needs. Choose to increase flexibility, improve strength, maintain good posture, or get fit and healthy!

WHY CHOOSE DAILY YOGA?

- Lose weight & burn fat
- Increase flexibility and get fit
- Decrease your stress with meditation 
- Personalized Custom Yoga Program
- Beginner friendly with Smart Coach to find courses to meet your goals.

MAIN FEATURES:
Daily Yoga challenges, Weekly New classes!

If you're a beginner, join the yoga challenges and see the result. Daily Yoga provides beginners-yoga series to help beginners learn the basics before diving into more advanced classes, sequences, and flows.

If you're advanced, new courses update weekly, so you won’t have to do the same yoga workouts over and over again.

Yoga for Weight Loss and Fat Burn!

Daily Yoga offers a variety of weight loss classes for different scenarios, including wall Pilates, chair yoga, and highly effective full-body yoga exercises to help you achieve visible results within days. Various difficulty levels, from beginner to advanced, allow you to practice step by step and easily achieve your weight loss goals. So whether you like yoga, wall pilates or want to do sofa yoga on your sofa/bed.

Easy to Follow!

Everyone, from beginner to advanced, can reap the benefits of yoga. Follow the detailed guidance in the app, and enjoy your exercise.

Smart Coach to Keep You Motivated!

The Smart Coach feature prevents having to search for a good class every day. Smart Coach creates a 28-day schedule of courses to help you reach your monthly goal.

Download Your Favorite Classes！

Download yoga classes, use them offline, and take them with you wherever you go. You can practice in your living room, hotel, beach, or even sitting on a chair or sofa. That's right, you can go for wall pilates, chair yoga, or sofa yoga, making it easy to stay active and healthy no matter where you are. 

Track and Record Your Progress!

Personal data can be tracked if you use different devices. With the smartwatch, you can track the exercise duration, calories burned, and heart rate to contribute to your activity rings and meet your daily goals. We integrate with HealthKit for you to export calories burned and exercise data.

Meditation for Mind and Body

Specially designed meditation classes to find inner peace. Boost your energy, release your stress, or follow a peaceful voice into a sweet dream.

Join The Worldwide Yoga Community!

Connect with 50M yogis around the world. Discuss your experience with each class, tag friends or other people doing the class, and encourage people to finish yoga challenges.

HealthKit

Daily Yoga integrates with HealthKit (Apple Health), so you can export calories burned and exercise data from Daily Yoga to HealthKit. We also perfectly support both Intel and Apple Silicon.

FOR MORE INFORMATION:
Terms of Use: https://www.dailyyoga.com/en/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://www.dailyyoga.com/en/privacy-policy.html

CONTACT:
Feel free to contact us anytime!
· App usage problems and suggestions: support@dailyyoga.com
· Business Cooperation: business@dailyyoga.com

Come to Life, Come to Yoga!

apps.description:
Fitzy – The Ultimate Workout & Training App
Transform your fitness journey with Fitzy, the all-in-one workout and training app for iPhone. Whether you're a beginner or a pro, Fitzy helps you achieve your health goals with personalized fitness plans, an extensive exercise library, and powerful tracking features.

Personalized Workout & Training Plans
Build custom workout plans or choose from professionally designed training programs. With 300+ exercises covering all muscle groups, you can create a plan that fits your lifestyle. Easily share plans via QR codes or import routines from friends to stay motivated.

Extensive Exercise Library
Explore a vast collection of exercises with step-by-step instructions and visuals to ensure proper form and maximize results. From strength training to cardio, Fitzy has everything you need for a complete fitness experience.

Advanced Fitness & Workout Tracker
Track your training sessions effortlessly! Log reps, sets, and weights while monitoring your progress through detailed graphs and statistics. Whether at the gym, home, or outdoors, Fitzy helps you stay on track with your workout goals.

Connect & Stay Motivated
Join the Fitzy community! Share workouts, exchange fitness plans, and compete with friends. Fitness is better together!

Why Choose Fitzy?
• Custom Plans – Tailor your fitness journey with personalized training routines
• 300+ Exercises – Covers strength, cardio, and gym workouts
• User-Friendly Design – Simple & intuitive for all fitness levels
• Detailed Progress Tracking – Visualize your improvements
• Community Features – Connect, share, and stay motivated

Fitness for Everyone
Fitzy offers premium fitness features without hidden costs. One of the top free fitness apps for iPhone, providing workouts, training plans, and tracking tools that compete with the best.

Perfect for All Fitness Levels
Whether you're training at home, gym, or on the go, Fitzy adapts to your routine. Your ultimate iOS workout companion that fits right in your pocket.

Start Your Fitness Journey Today
Join thousands achieving their fitness goals with Fitzy! Download now and take the first step toward a stronger, healthier you.

This app includes in-app purchases
